Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.91,0:00:31.78,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 玛丽安太太 - 有九码半的吗?\N{\rEng}- Mrs. Mariann. - You have the nine and a half?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.78,0:00:33.24,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 您运气真好 - 噢 我好激动\N{\rEng}- Yeah, you're a lucky lady. - Oh, I'm excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.24,0:00:35.29,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,最后的一双 让我看看这双美脚\N{\rEng}Last pair. Let me see those beautiful feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:37.68,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,225)\fs180\fsp50\fscx130\c&HF7FFFF&\3c&HADCDFF&\bord1\blur0.2\b1}纽约
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.25,0:00:39.91,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,右脚还合适吗?\N{\rEng}The right foot's all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.92,0:00:41.21,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这就对了 伸进去\N{\rEng}There you go. Get it in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.42,0:00:44.13,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 太挤了 - 没事 没关系\N{\rEng}- They're too tight. - It's okay. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.13,0:00:46.71,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 这真是九码半? - 确实是九码半\N{\rEng}- Are these the nine and a half? - These are the nine and a half, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.71,0:00:47.92,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,有大一码的吗?\N{\rEng}Do you have the next size?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:50.22,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,克里布鲁克没货了 这就是我不待见这牌子的原因\N{\rEng}No, not in a Kerrybrooke. But that's why I don't like Kerrybrooke,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.22,0:00:53.18,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,尺码偏小 简直是给洋娃娃做的\N{\rEng}because they fit really small. They're made for dolls or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.18,0:00:55.31,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 还是太紧 - 行 脱了吧 没事\N{\rEng}- They're too tight. - Okay, take 'em off. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.93,0:00:57.52,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 试过活力牌吗? - 没\N{\rEng}- You ever try Vitality? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.52,0:00:58.68,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,马上就来招呼您\N{\rEng}I'll be right with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.94,0:01:01.64,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,打扰下 抱歉\N{\rEng}Excuse me. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.65,0:01:04.56,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我前几天在那位戴眼镜的先生那买了一双鞋\N{\rEng}I bought a pair of shoes here the other day from him, with the glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.57,0:01:05.65,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 马蒂 - 怎么?\N{\rEng}- Marty. - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.65,0:01:07.53,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这位女士说找你买过鞋\N{\rEng}This woman said she bought a pair of shoes from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.24,0:01:10.70,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,噢 对 买了双棕色玛丽珍鞋 对吧?\N{\rEng}Oh, yeah. You bought the brown Mary Janes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.70,0:01:13.11,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,没错 特别好 我直接穿着走出门的\N{\rEng}Yeah, I did. They're great. I wore them out of the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.12,0:01:15.24,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 好的 - 所以我旧鞋落这了\N{\rEng}- Okay. - So I left my old ones here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.24,0:01:16.41,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,行 长什么样?\N{\rEng}Okay. What did they look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:18.45,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,拼色跟鞋 雕花款\N{\rEng}They're two-toned pumps, wingtips.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.45,0:01:20.37,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 劳埃德 见她鞋了吗? - 没见\N{\rEng}- Lloyd, did you see her shoes? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.37,0:01:22.67,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,有没有可能你把鞋装进我试穿的其他鞋盒里\N{\rEng}Is it possible that you maybe put them in one of the boxes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.67,0:01:25.42,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,重新上架了?\N{\rEng}of the other shoes that I was trying on and restocked them?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.42,0:01:27.55,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,行吧 呃...\N{\rEng}Okay. All right. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.55,0:01:29.59,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,介意让我同事帮您找找吗?\N{\rEng}Do you mind if my colleague helps you out for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:31.72,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,劳埃德 帮玛丽安找找\N{\rEng}Lloyd. Can you help with Mariann here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:32.84,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,没问题\N{\rEng}Sure. Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:34.47,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我们去地下室看看 跟我来\N{\rEng}Yeah, we'll check the basement. Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.47,0:01:35.97,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,谢谢 借过\N{\rEng}Thank you. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.97,0:01:37.43,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,劳埃德会帮您的 拿几双活力牌试试\N{\rEng}Lloyd's gonna help you. Get the Vitalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.43,0:01:38.89,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,行 价格我再考虑下\N{\rEng}Okay. I'll think about the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.89,0:01:40.64,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,马上就来 忙完手头这点\N{\rEng}I'll be right with you. Let me finish up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.64,0:01:41.77,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,好的 谢谢\N{\rEng}Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.77,0:01:42.90,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 干嘛? - 嘘\N{\rEng}- What? - Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.69,0:01:46.11,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 马蒂 - 操 该死\N{\rEng}- Marty. - Ah, fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.11,0:01:47.61,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,给你看个宝贝 过来\N{\rEng}I wanna show you something. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.61,0:01:49.61,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 啥? - 等会 蹲低点 蹲下\N{\rEng}- What? - One second. Just get low. Go low.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.61,0:01:50.99,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,干嘛非得蹲着?\N{\rEng}Why do I have to get low?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.07,0:01:55.49,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 怎么样? - 马蒂 看看我给你弄到了什么\N{\rEng}- How you doing? - Marty, look what I got for ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.49,0:01:56.49,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这是啥?\N{\rEng}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:01:58.16,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧\N{\rEng}Check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.24,0:02:00.54,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这看的是啥?\N{\rEng}What am I looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:01.54,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,翻过来\N{\rEng}Turn it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.58,0:02:06.00,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 经理? - 经理\N{\rEng}- Manager? - Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:07.25,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,得了吧 默里\N{\rEng}Come on, Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:09.34,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不管怎样 千万别跟劳埃德说\N{\rEng}Whatever you do, just don't tell Lloyd about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.34,0:02:10.76,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,听着 我跟你说明白了\N{\rEng}Look, I've been very clear with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.76,0:02:13.97,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我不是想冒犯 你的成就确实令人敬佩\N{\rEng}I'm not trying to be disrespectful. You built something very commendable here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.97,0:02:16.34,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我现在不想谈这个\N{\rEng}I don't wanna-- I don't wanna discuss this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.35,0:02:18.18,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,停下 听我说\N{\rEng}Stop. Stop. Let me say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.18,0:02:20.72,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,亲眼看到这一切 真是种洗礼\N{\rEng}It's been good for my soul to see this up close and personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:22.81,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 但我不是卖鞋的 - 我不想谈这个\N{\rEng}- But I'm not a shoe salesman. - I don't wanna discuss this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.81,0:02:25.69,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我不是卖鞋的 - 我不想谈这个 行吗?\N{\rEng}- I'm not a shoe salesman. - I don't wanna discuss this, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.69,0:02:27.77,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我非得谈谈 等我出差回来 这一切就结束了\N{\rEng}I do wanna discuss it, 'cause when I'm back from my trip, this is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:28.86,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我不会回来继续干这个的\N{\rEng}I'm not coming back and doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.86,0:02:30.98,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,说到这 能把账结了吗? 我得买机票\N{\rEng}Speaking of which, can we settle up now? I gotta buy my plane ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.98,0:02:32.07,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,关门时再结\N{\rEng}We'll settle at closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.07,0:02:33.36,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我想趁休息去找旅行社\N{\rEng}I wanted to see the travel agent on my break.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:35.03,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你午休完肯定就不回来了\N{\rEng}You'll never come back after your lunch break.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.03,0:02:36.45,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你就是这么看我的?\N{\rEng}That's what you think of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.16,0:02:39.03,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 对 - 你觉得我会一去不返?\N{\rEng}- Yes. - You think I would go and not come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:40.91,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,对 我说了关门再结 行吗?\N{\rEng}Yes. I said settle at closing, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.91,0:02:42.83,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 就这样? - 对 就这样 再见\N{\rEng}- That's it? - Yeah, that's it. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:43.96,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\rEng}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.25,0:02:46.67,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 别闹了 - 等等 等我一下\N{\rEng}- Come on. - Wait. Just wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.93,0:03:01.64,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我正要... 我正要去找你\N{\rEng}I was about... I was about to come to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:03.81,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不行 艾拉病了在家\N{\rEng}No, Ira's home sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:05.48,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 喔 喔 喔 我可不能生病 - 什么?\N{\rEng}- Whoa, whoa, whoa. I can't get sick. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:06.69,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我还得打锦标赛\N{\rEng}I got the championships.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.69,0:03:09.31,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,没事 是食物中毒 食物中毒\N{\rEng}No, it's food poisoning. It's food poisoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:34.72,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,真想把你塞进行李里带走\N{\rEng}I wish I could hide you in my luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:39.30,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我好想跟你一起去\N{\rEng}I wanna come with you so bad.
