Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.92,0:43:45.00,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,打扰下\N{\rEng}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.83,0:43:46.84,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\rEng}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.86,0:44:13.19,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,别在我房间吃喝 会招虫子\N{\rEng}Please don't eat or drink in my room. It attracts bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.20,0:44:15.32,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我进屋只是为了打扫 仅此而已\N{\rEng}I just go in there to clean. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.42,0:44:27.25,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,看来你并不欢迎我\N{\rEng}Well, you don't seem happy to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.25,0:44:28.96,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,是啊 看来你也不怎么欢迎我\N{\rEng}Yeah, and you don't seem happy to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.96,0:44:31.38,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,那么 你现在打算住这儿吗?\N{\rEng}So, now are you going to be staying here?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.38,0:44:33.01,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,怎么 不行吗? 别担心\N{\rEng}What, is that not okay? Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.01,0:44:34.76,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,过几周我就挪窝 不招你烦了\N{\rEng}I'll be out of your hair in a few weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.76,0:44:36.22,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,别犯傻\N{\rEng}Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.89,0:44:40.51,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 怎么? 过几周有什么事? - 世锦赛\N{\rEng}- Why? What's in a few weeks? - World Championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.51,0:44:42.64,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 在哪儿办? - 东京\N{\rEng}- So, where's that gonna be? - Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.52,0:44:44.93,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,日本东京?\N{\rEng}Tokyo, Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.94,0:44:46.94,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你是在问我东京是不是在日本吗?\N{\rEng}Are you asking me if Tokyo's in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.90,0:44:49.69,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你是认真的吗?\N{\rEng}Is that a serious question?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.69,0:44:51.65,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我看你累坏了\N{\rEng}You look very tired to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.65,0:44:54.28,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,是啊 我刚跑了大半个地球 能不累吗\N{\rEng}Yeah, 'cause I just traveled halfway around the world. I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.28,0:44:56.74,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我很忙 忙着工作 忙着搞钱\N{\rEng}I was busy. I was working. I was making money.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.96,0:45:10.08,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,趁这楼里的人都在上班\N{\rEng}You know, while everybody is at work in the building,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.09,0:45:14.42,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,正是你舒舒服服洗个热水长澡的好时候\N{\rEng}it would be a good time for you to take a nice, long, hot shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.42,0:45:15.76,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 给 - 这是什么?\N{\rEng}- Here. - What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.76,0:45:16.97,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我给你带了东西 - 嗯\N{\rEng}- I got you something. - Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.44,0:45:37.53,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这是埃及金字塔上的原件\N{\rEng}It's from an original Egyptian pyramid.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.45,0:45:41.70,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,那可是我们建的\N{\rEng}We built that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.04,0:45:44.04,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,行吧\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.43,0:46:00.51,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿 利维 你长高了不少啊\N{\rEng}Hey, Levi. You got a lot taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.51,0:46:01.93,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我没有 - 怎么没有\N{\rEng}- No, I didn't. - Yeah, you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.35,0:46:07.93,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 抱歉 找我有事? - 对 跟我走\N{\rEng}- Excuse me. Can I help you? - Yeah. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.94,0:46:09.52,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 走 赶紧的 - 嘿! 你干嘛?\N{\rEng}- Come on, come on. - Hey! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.52,0:46:11.81,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 跟我走 快走 - 不! 你他妈到底在干嘛?\N{\rEng}- Let's go, let's go. Let's go. - No! What the fuck are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.81,0:46:13.19,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你被捕了 - 我没有!\N{\rEng}- You're under arrest. - No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.19,0:46:15.23,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 被捕了 过来 别乱动! - 凭什么逮捕我?\N{\rEng}- Yes, you are. Come here. Stop moving! - What am I under arrest for?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.23,0:46:16.90,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 那是我的洗漱用品! 噢! - 你被捕了\N{\rEng}- That's my toiletries! Ow! - You're under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.90,0:46:18.49,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 犯了什么事? - 持械抢劫 走吧\N{\rEng}- For what? - Armed robbery. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.49,0:46:19.82,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,持械抢-- 你胡说什么呢?\N{\rEng}Armed rob-- What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.82,0:46:21.24,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,再乱动就要伤着你自己了!\N{\rEng}You're gonna hurt yourself if you keep moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.24,0:46:22.32,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 到底怎么回事? - 走\N{\rEng}- What is going on? - Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.32,0:46:24.99,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 默里 我妈在哪? 默里 - 我让她先出去待会儿\N{\rEng}- Murray, where's my mother? Murray. - I asked her to leave for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.99,0:46:28.20,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你让她-- 到底他妈怎么回事? 我要被抓了! 救我!\N{\rEng}You told her-- What the fuck is going on? I'm getting arrested! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.21,0:46:30.87,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,萨尔 萨尔 我想跟他单独谈谈 麻烦了 先走吧\N{\rEng}Sal, Sal. I wanna talk to him in private. Excuse us. Just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.87,0:46:32.38,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 萨尔? 你认识这人? - 要我怎么做?\N{\rEng}- Sal? You know this guy? - What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.38,0:46:34.04,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 先去后面待会儿 - 行\N{\rEng}- Just go in the back for a while. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.04,0:46:35.25,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,关上门\N{\rEng}Close the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.25,0:46:37.05,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,行 要是闹起来了就喊一声\N{\rEng}All right, if it gets crazy just holler.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.05,0:46:39.67,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,到底他妈怎么回事 默里? 我拿的那笔钱是你欠我的\N{\rEng}What the fuck is going on, Murray? That money I took, you owed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.68,0:46:41.80,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不 不 不 不 那是你持枪抢走的钱\N{\rEng}No, no, no, no. It was money you stole at gunpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.80,0:46:43.85,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 不 你答应过我... 抱歉 - 不 你根本没...\N{\rEng}- No, you promised me... Excuse me. - No, you didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.85,0:46:45.76,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,那是我的钱 结果你拿走了--\N{\rEng}That was my money and you took--
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.76,0:46:48.14,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你答应过要把那笔钱给我的 我没... 我干嘛要编瞎话?\N{\rEng}You promised me that money. I'm not... Why would I make this up?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.14,0:46:50.60,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 那是去英国的路费 - 你那趟旅行怎么着了?\N{\rEng}- It was money for my trip to England. - What happened on your trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.60,0:46:52.06,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,什么叫怎么着了?\N{\rEng}What do you mean, what happened on my trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.06,0:46:53.19,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你输了! - 我没输!\N{\rEng}- You lost! - No, I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.19,0:46:54.73,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你就是输了! - 从哪儿听说的?\N{\rEng}- You did! - Where did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.73,0:46:56.40,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 不 我是被耍了 - 你知不知道有多少次\N{\rEng}- No, I got cheated against. - Do you know how many times
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.40,0:46:58.15,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 在大半夜里... - 行了 别扯淡了\N{\rEng}- in the middle of the night... - No, no. Stop with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.15,0:47:00.11,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 闭嘴 听我说! - 少教训我\N{\rEng}- Shut up and listen to me! - Don't lecture me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.11,0:47:01.24,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,闭嘴!\N{\rEng}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.74,0:47:05.16,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你根本不知道我被吵醒过多少次去保释你\N{\rEng}You don't know how many times I had to get woken up and bail you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.16,0:47:06.37,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我什么时候求你干过那事?\N{\rEng}When did I ask you to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.37,0:47:08.41,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我什么时候找你帮过忙? - 你确实没求过我\N{\rEng}- When have I ever asked for your help? - You never asked me to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.41,0:47:09.75,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 就是啊! - 但我还是做了\N{\rEng}- Exactly! - But I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.75,0:47:12.54,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,现在 你得像个大人样了\N{\rEng}And now, you're gonna be a big boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.54,0:47:14.04,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 轮到你了 - 像个大人样?\N{\rEng}- It's your turn. - A big boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.04,0:47:16.71,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你真跟我这么说话? - 没错 听着...\N{\rEng}- Did you really just say that to me? - Yeah. Yeah, you know, look...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.71,0:47:19.46,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我不可能养你妈一辈子\N{\rEng}I can't support your mother for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.46,0:47:21.22,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你不用养 - 噢 是吗? 凭什么?\N{\rEng}- You're not gonna have to. - Oh, yeah? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.22,0:47:23.59,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 因为我要承担起来了 - 你承担? 怎么承担?\N{\rEng}- Because I'm gonna step up. - You're gonna step up? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.59,0:47:25.85,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你没法想象 她会住在第五大道\N{\rEng}In a way you can't imagine. She's gonna be living on Fifth Avenue
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.85,0:47:27.64,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,住在有电梯的高档公寓里\N{\rEng}in an apartment and building with a elevator,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.64,0:47:30.43,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,还有专门开电梯的人 随叫随到\N{\rEng}and a man who works in the elevator that takes her every time she needs to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.43,0:47:32.39,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,行了 行了 听着\N{\rEng}Sure, sure, sure. All right, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.39,0:47:34.48,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我给你两个选择 行吗?\N{\rEng}I'm gonna give you two options, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.48,0:47:36.52,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我想你会喜欢第一个\N{\rEng}I think you'll like the first one.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.52,0:47:38.19,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你回店里上班\N{\rEng}You come back to the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.19,0:47:40.74,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这回 别再扯淡了\N{\rEng}This time, no more bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.74,0:47:43.57,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,别再搞这些乒乓球的荒唐事了 行吗?\N{\rEng}None of this ping-pong mishegoss, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.57,0:47:45.53,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我会给你更大的权责\N{\rEng}I'm gonna give you much more responsibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.53,0:47:49.04,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,因为说实话 你是个了不起的推销员\N{\rEng}because truth be told, you're an amazing salesman.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.04,0:47:50.83,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我能把鞋卖给残疾人\N{\rEng}I could sell shoes to an amputee.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.83,0:47:52.75,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,那又怎样? 另一个选择呢?\N{\rEng}So what? What's the other option?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.75,0:47:54.21,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我控告你\N{\rEng}I press charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.21,0:47:56.33,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 劳埃德是证人... - 你不会那么干的\N{\rEng}- Lloyd is a witness... - You're not doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.34,0:47:57.42,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,...你得去蹲大牢!\N{\rEng}...and you go to jail!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.42,0:47:59.75,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,真的? 对你亲外甥这么狠? 你疯了吗?\N{\rEng}Really? You'd do that to your own kin? Are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.76,0:48:02.80,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 走着瞧... 这是自作自受 - 嘿 萨尔! 萨尔!\N{\rEng}- We'll see... You took it upon yourself. - Hey, Sal! Sal!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.80,0:48:04.76,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 干嘛? - 他现在给你开多少钱?\N{\rEng}- What? - How much is he paying you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.76,0:48:06.26,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你在说什么 给我开钱?\N{\rEng}What are you talking about, paying me?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.26,0:48:07.89,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我舅舅花多少钱雇你来吓唬我?\N{\rEng}How much is my uncle paying for you to scare me?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.89,0:48:10.31,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不管多少 我出双倍让你给我跪下舔干净\N{\rEng}'Cause whatever it is, I'll double it for you to suck my dick.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.31,0:48:12.02,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 什么? - 给我舔\N{\rEng}- What? - Suck my dick.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.02,0:48:13.43,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你口臭太他妈难闻了 - 嘴放干净点 你这--\N{\rEng}- You have terrible breath. - Watch your mouth, you--
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.44,0:48:15.52,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 噢! 操! - 走 咱们现在就走\N{\rEng}- Ow! Fuck! - Let's go. We're going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.52,0:48:17.48,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 他刚才打我! - 住手 拜托停下\N{\rEng}- He just hit me! - Stop. Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.48,0:48:18.61,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 默里 他打我 - 停下\N{\rEng}- Murray, he hit me. - Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.61,0:48:20.36,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我们都商量好了\N{\rEng}We worked everything out.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.36,0:48:22.61,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你在别的屋子 没听见 我们已经谈妥了\N{\rEng}You were in the other room. You didn't hear. We already worked it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.61,0:48:24.20,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 他会赔偿一切 - 畜生\N{\rEng}- He's paying back everything. - Animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.20,0:48:26.36,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他把钱给我了 万事大吉\N{\rEng}He gave me the money, and everything's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.37,0:48:28.24,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你从哪弄来的? - 我从你行李箱里拿的\N{\rEng}- Where did you get that? - I got it from your luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.24,0:48:31.41,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗? 那是我去日本的钱!\N{\rEng}Are you out of your mind? That's my money for Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.41,0:48:34.08,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你他妈疯了吗? - 走 赶紧走\N{\rEng}- Are you out of your fucking mind? - Let's go. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.08,0:48:36.42,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,就把他带去市局 妈的! 带他走!\N{\rEng}Just take him downtown, damn it! Take him downtown!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.42,0:48:38.88,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 行了 好了! 我不闹了! - 你玩完了 彻底完了\N{\rEng}- Okay. All right! Okay! I'll stop! - You're done. You're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.88,0:48:40.38,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 拜托 停下 住手 - 跟我走\N{\rEng}- Please. Stop. Stop. - Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.38,0:48:42.71,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 行了 放他走 放开他 - 放他走?\N{\rEng}- All right. Let him go. Let him go. - Let him go?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.71,0:48:44.55,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 放开他 让他走 - 坐好\N{\rEng}- Let him go. Let him go. - Sit up.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.26,0:48:48.09,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,听着 道个歉\N{\rEng}Listen, apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.10,0:48:50.22,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,行 抱歉 我错了\N{\rEng}Okay, I'm sorry. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.22,0:48:51.47,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,给他解开手铐\N{\rEng}Take his cuffs off.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.27,0:48:54.64,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 咱们接下来的打算 听好了? - 行\N{\rEng}- This is what's gonna happen, okay? - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.48,0:48:58.94,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,咱们去花园咖啡馆见你妈\N{\rEng}We're gonna meet your mom at the Garden Café.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.65,0:49:01.86,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,咱们好好吃顿饭\N{\rEng}We're gonna have a really nice dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.86,0:49:04.15,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,之前的破事儿就翻篇了 行吗?\N{\rEng}And let's just put all this shit behind us, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.15,0:49:05.24,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,行 没问题\N{\rEng}Okay. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.24,0:49:07.82,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我错了 我错了 真心对不住 - 你知错了?\N{\rEng}- I'm sorry, I'm sorry. I'm sorry. - You're sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.82,0:49:09.87,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,剩下的事儿咱们去解决 赶紧穿衣服\N{\rEng}We'll take care of everything. Just get dressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.87,0:49:11.95,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 好了 舅舅爱你 - 行 我也爱你\N{\rEng}- Come on. I love you. - All right. I love you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.20,0:49:16.21,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你那外甥就是坨狗屎 你知道吧?\N{\rEng}Your nephew's a piece of shit, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.21,0:49:18.08,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,噢 天呐 实在对不住\N{\rEng}Oh, Jesus. I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.96,0:49:20.34,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这儿再给你十块\N{\rEng}Here another ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.88,0:49:21.88,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,行 没问题\N{\rEng}Yeah, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.75,0:49:24.51,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,花园咖啡馆? 你都点什么?\N{\rEng}Garden Café, huh? What do you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.51,0:49:26.17,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,熏牛肉啊 还能有什么?\N{\rEng}The pastrami, what else?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.18,0:49:27.72,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 噢 熏牛肉 - 你点什么?\N{\rEng}- Ah, pastrami. - What do you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.72,0:49:28.80,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,烤牛肉\N{\rEng}Roast beef.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.80,0:49:30.14,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 烤牛肉? - 昂\N{\rEng}- Roast beef? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.14,0:49:31.26,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,外行条子!\N{\rEng}Goyishecop!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.15,0:49:40.15,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\rEng}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.23,0:49:43.53,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,开门 赶紧的\N{\rEng}Open up. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.61,0:49:46.03,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 把它撞开 - 冲进去?\N{\rEng}- Break it down. - Break it in?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.95,0:49:49.95,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,操!\N{\rEng}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.49,0:49:52.41,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿! 你往哪跑?\N{\rEng}Hey! Where you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.41,0:49:53.41,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\rEng}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.29,0:49:55.91,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 出什么事了? - 他跳窗跑了\N{\rEng}- What happened? - He went out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.91,0:49:57.71,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 什么? 等等! - 弗兰基!\N{\rEng}- What? Wait! - Frankie!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.33,0:50:00.13,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 什么? - 他正顺着消防梯往下爬呢\N{\rEng}- What? - He's coming down the escape right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.21,0:50:03.34,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他在那儿! 顺着消防梯下去了!\N{\rEng}There he goes! Down the escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.34,0:50:05.59,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 噢 操 - 追 追 追!\N{\rEng}- Oh, shit. - Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.86,0:50:29.40,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我去后头打个电话 - 拿稳了\N{\rEng}- I'm just gonna use the phone in the back. - You hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.37,0:50:35.04,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,瞧见他有多喜欢你了吗?\N{\rEng}See how much he likes you?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.62,0:50:42.08,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 喂?- 嘿 沃利 怎么样? 我是马蒂\N{\rEng}- Hello?- Hey, Wally. How you doing? It's Marty.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.08,0:50:44.09,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 今晚出车吗? - 废话 当然出\N{\rEng}- Are you working tonight? - Of course I'm working.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.09,0:50:46.21,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,行 太棒了 带着车 尽可能多带点现金\N{\rEng}Okay, great. Bring your cab and as much cash as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.21,0:50:48.67,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,到28街的海尔西找我 听明白没?\N{\rEng}I want you to meet me at The Halsey on 28th Street, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.67,0:50:51.01,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,什么? 你又想去混场子了?\N{\rEng}What? You wanna go hustling again?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.01,0:50:52.18,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,没错 正是这意思\N{\rEng}Yeah, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.18,0:50:54.01,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,不不不 上回我被虐惨了\N{\rEng}No, no, no. I got my ass kicked last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.01,0:50:55.43,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,咱们大老远跑去斯塔滕岛\N{\rEng}We went all the way to Staten Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.43,0:50:57.97,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,结果十分钟不到 他们就认出你来了\N{\rEng}and within ten minutes, they recognized you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.98,0:51:00.89,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,没事 咱们去昆提过的新泽西那地儿\N{\rEng}It's fine. We're gonna go to that place that Quinn was talking about in Jersey.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.89,0:51:02.02,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,那可不是什么好主意\N{\rEng}That's a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.02,0:51:04.40,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 这是你的新宠物 - 不 妈 我想要犰狳\N{\rEng}- That's your new pet. - No, Mom, I want the armadillo.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.40,0:51:05.48,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不 我已经--\N{\rEng}No, I already--
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.48,0:51:07.61,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,知道吗? 我就给你买那只犰狳\N{\rEng}You know what? I'm just gonna get you the armadillo.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.36,0:51:11.32,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我把它给你 然后你自己决定 行吗?\N{\rEng}I'm gonna give him to you, and then you can make a decision. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.32,0:51:12.61,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,它们不是爬行动物 是哺乳动物\N{\rEng}They're not reptiles. They're mammals.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.61,0:51:15.12,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,行 太棒了 你真是个好人 一个半小时后见\N{\rEng}Okay, great. You're a beautiful man. I'll see you in an hour and a half.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.12,0:51:16.58,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 哪儿?- 海尔西 就这样 爱你\N{\rEng}- Where?- At the Halsey. Okay. I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.58,0:51:17.74,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,谢了 拜\N{\rEng}Thank you. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.33,0:51:19.41,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,很好 给你\N{\rEng}Good. Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.41,0:51:21.71,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,拜托 有后门或者别的小道能走吗?\N{\rEng}Is there a way I can go out the back or something, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.71,0:51:24.58,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,干嘛? 你干嘛这么看着我?\N{\rEng}What? Why are you looking at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.59,0:51:26.04,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你就不打算跟我说点什么吗?\N{\rEng}Aren't you gonna say something to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.59,0:51:28.96,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,说什么 恭喜吗?\N{\rEng}What, congratulations?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.55,0:51:31.51,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 恭喜? - 对\N{\rEng}- Congratulations? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.51,0:51:33.13,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你开玩笑吗? - 你想让我说什么?\N{\rEng}- Are you kidding me? - What do you want me to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.14,0:51:35.14,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我找了你整整八个月\N{\rEng}I've been trying to get in contact with you for eight months.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.14,0:51:36.93,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我知道你想干嘛 没用的\N{\rEng}I see what you're trying to do. It's not gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.93,0:51:38.18,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你说什么? - 那种不是我的\N{\rEng}- Excuse me? - That's not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.18,0:51:40.60,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 绝对是你的 - 不可能 我都是拔出来的\N{\rEng}- It is absolutely yours. - No, it's not. I pull out.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.60,0:51:42.02,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,艾拉也拔出来吗?\N{\rEng}Does Ira pull out?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.02,0:51:44.02,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你想让我怎么回? - 很简单的问题\N{\rEng}- What do you want me to say to that? - It's a simple question.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.02,0:51:45.56,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他跟你干那事儿的时候也拔出来吗?\N{\rEng}Does he pull out when he has sex with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.56,0:51:46.94,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 回答我 - 你非要我回答这个?\N{\rEng}- Answer it. - You want me to answer that?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.94,0:51:48.61,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,对! 回答我! 他在那什么的时候...\N{\rEng}Yes! Answer it. Does he pull out when he...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.61,0:51:52.70,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起 对不起\N{\rEng}I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.70,0:51:54.66,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我现在一团糟 瑞秋 真的乱透了\N{\rEng}I'm a mess right now. I'm really a mess, Rachel.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.66,0:51:56.24,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,顺便说下 我在伦敦输了--\N{\rEng}I lost in London, by the way--
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.24,0:51:57.24,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿!\N{\rEng}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.37,0:52:00.37,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\rEng}God.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.58,0:52:04.75,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这是干嘛?\N{\rEng}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.96,0:52:08.46,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他爸爸过世了\N{\rEng}His father died.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.51,0:52:13.47,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 扯淡! - 她是我八岁就认识的朋友\N{\rEng}- Bullshit! - This is my friend since I was eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.47,0:52:14.59,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我在跟你说话吗?\N{\rEng}Am I talking to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.59,0:52:16.43,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,艾拉 我八岁就认识她了\N{\rEng}Ira, I've known her since I was eight years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.43,0:52:18.31,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我爸刚走 她在安慰我\N{\rEng}My father just died. She was consoling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.85,0:52:20.43,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 没事\N{\rEng}Honey, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.43,0:52:23.14,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 闭嘴! 别碰我! - 你就这么跟老婆说话?\N{\rEng}- Shut up! Don't touch me! - That's how you talk to your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.14,0:52:24.98,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,对 我就这么跟她说话\N{\rEng}Yeah, that's how I talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.98,0:52:26.06,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,行\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.06,0:52:27.73,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,别 别 别! 来啊 继续说\N{\rEng}No, no, no! Come on. Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.73,0:52:29.11,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 继续啊 - 马蒂 算了 别说了\N{\rEng}- Keep going. - Marty, just stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.11,0:52:31.98,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我要把他脑门上那条他妈的一字眉给撕了!\N{\rEng}I'll rip that unibrow right off his fucking forehead!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.99,0:52:34.53,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你想动手? 跟个大猩猩似的?\N{\rEng}You wanna get physical? Like an ape?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.66,0:52:40.87,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,艾拉\N{\rEng}Ira.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.87,0:52:43.41,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,艾拉! 快回来 你干嘛呢?\N{\rEng}Ira! Come back inside. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.41,0:52:45.67,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,谁快去他妈的把条子叫来?\N{\rEng}Somebody get the fucking cops over here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.67,0:52:47.67,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你干了什么? - 操! 我得闪人了\N{\rEng}- What did you do? - Fuck! I gotta get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.67,0:52:48.92,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你跑什么? 条子追你干嘛?\N{\rEng}Why are you running from the cops?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.92,0:52:50.34,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,快点 他就在这儿!\N{\rEng}Come on, he's right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.34,0:52:51.84,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,没后门能溜吗?\N{\rEng}There's no way out the back?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.84,0:52:54.38,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 什么? 什么-- - 拜托! 快点 瑞秋! 精神点\N{\rEng}- What? What-- - Please! Come on. Rachel! Focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.38,0:52:55.84,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,通往后院 走\N{\rEng}it leads out the back. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.84,0:52:57.39,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,行 行 谢谢 谢谢\N{\rEng}Okay. Okay. Thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.39,0:52:59.35,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,回头再跟你说 回头再说\N{\rEng}I'll tell you later. I'll tell you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.33,0:53:33.34,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,哥几个 见着个戴眼镜的白人小子打这儿路过吗?\N{\rEng}Guys, you see a white kid with glasses come through here?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.13,0:53:35.67,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,没人看见他?\N{\rEng}Nobody saw him?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.22,0:53:37.68,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,听不懂英语 昂?\N{\rEng}No English, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.68,0:53:40.05,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,如需继续通话 请投币五分\N{\rEng}Please insert a nickel if you'd like to continue the conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.05,0:53:42.22,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,五分? 电话要断了\N{\rEng}A nickel? They're gonna cut us off.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.22,0:53:43.64,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你有五分吗? - 没\N{\rEng}- Do you have a nickel? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.64,0:53:46.27,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,妈 我没撒谎 我保证这是最后一次\N{\rEng}Mom, I'm not lying. I promise you this will be the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.27,0:53:49.02,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我眼瞎了吗 那是他妈的"小老鼠"?\N{\rEng}Are my eyes broke, or is that motherfucking Mouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.02,0:53:50.19,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 谢了 - 怎么着 宝贝?\N{\rEng}- Thank you. - What's up, baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.19,0:53:52.32,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,太谢谢了 真是帮大忙了 谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you so much. I really appreciate it. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.32,0:53:53.61,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,马蒂 你闻着像股鱼腥味\N{\rEng}You smell like a fish, Marty.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.61,0:53:55.82,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,所以咱们得开个房 我得洗个澡\N{\rEng}That's why we gotta get a hotel room. I need to get a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.82,0:53:57.61,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿 哥们 弄个房间 行吗?\N{\rEng}How you doing? Hey, can we get a hotel room, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.61,0:53:59.24,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 四块钱 - 你刚还说三块呢\N{\rEng}- Four dollars. - You said it was three dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.24,0:54:02.24,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 那是上个房间的价格 现在四块 - 怎么现在变四块了?\N{\rEng}- That was for the last room. It's four. - Why is it four dollars now?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.24,0:54:03.91,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,借我四块 我保证还你\N{\rEng}Let me get four bucks. I'll pay you back, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.91,0:54:05.83,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我丑话说在前 咱们一共就十块本钱\N{\rEng}I'm telling you right now, we only got ten to play with.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.83,0:54:06.91,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你就带了十块?\N{\rEng}You brought ten dollars?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.91,0:54:09.21,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你才提前一小时通知我 - 那咱们怎么赢钱?\N{\rEng}- You gave me a hour notice. - How are we supposed to make money?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.21,0:54:10.50,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我得养娃呢! 我就是个操蛋的出租车司机\N{\rEng}I got kids! I'm a fucking taxi driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.50,0:54:12.34,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,有便宜点的房吗? 差点儿没事\N{\rEng}Do you have a cheaper room? It doesn't have to be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.34,0:54:14.80,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,五楼有一间 但不能洗澡\N{\rEng}There's a room on the fifth floor, but you can't use the shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.80,0:54:16.38,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 行 那个多少? - 两块五\N{\rEng}- Okay, how much is that? - Two fifty.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.38,0:54:18.17,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,拿三块给我 谢谢\N{\rEng}Let me get three dollars. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.18,0:54:19.97,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你最好还我 算你走运 我还拿你当哥们\N{\rEng}You better pay me back. You lucky I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.97,0:54:22.05,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 吉米 吉米 - 待会从赢的钱里扣\N{\rEng}- Jimmy. Jimmy. - It's coming out your winnings.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.05,0:54:23.14,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,钥匙给我\N{\rEng}Give me the keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.14,0:54:24.47,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,什么味儿?\N{\rEng}What's that smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.47,0:54:26.47,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,噢 我的天! 操\N{\rEng}Oh, my God! Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.48,0:54:28.31,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 哇! 那是什么? - 噢 我的天!\N{\rEng}- Wow! What is that? - Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.31,0:54:29.85,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他出了点小意外\N{\rEng}He had a little accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.85,0:54:31.69,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,天呐! 他拉了个大的\N{\rEng}God! He had an enormous accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.69,0:54:33.31,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,太恶心了\N{\rEng}That's horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.32,0:54:34.73,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 闻着像坨屎! - 操!\N{\rEng}- Smells like shit! - Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.73,0:54:36.19,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,吉米 你臭得像坨屎\N{\rEng}Jimmy, you smell like shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.19,0:54:38.49,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 是你口臭还是那狗臭? - 能把钥匙给我了吗?\N{\rEng}- Is that your breath or the dog? - Can I get my key, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.49,0:54:41.07,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,别带着那狗进电梯 走楼梯\N{\rEng}Do not go in the elevator with that dog. Take the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.07,0:54:43.62,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 跟我开玩笑呢? - 给那狗洗洗\N{\rEng}- Are you kidding me? - Wash that dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.62,0:54:44.83,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,再见 吉米\N{\rEng}Goodbye, Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.70,0:54:48.66,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 她肚子多大了 马蒂? - 很大 挺大的\N{\rEng}- How big is she, Marty? - Very big. Big.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.66,0:54:49.79,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,明天就生吗?\N{\rEng}Is she popping out tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.79,0:54:52.12,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我哪知道什么时候生 听着 我只知道孩子不是我的\N{\rEng}I don't know when she's popping out. Look, all I know is it's not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.13,0:54:53.71,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,她有阴谋 你不像我这么了解她\N{\rEng}She has an agenda. You don't know her like I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.71,0:54:55.71,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,她困在一段操蛋的婚姻里 生活过得一塌糊涂\N{\rEng}She's stuck in a miserable marriage. She has a horrible life.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.71,0:54:56.80,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,她就是想赖在我头上\N{\rEng}She's trying to pin it down on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.80,0:54:58.59,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,从咱们八岁起 她就想把我套牢\N{\rEng}Since we were eight years old, she's trying to get me stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.59,0:55:00.17,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 就为了套你这穷光蛋? - 没错\N{\rEng}- Your bummy ass? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.18,0:55:01.30,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,也是 她确实疯\N{\rEng}Yeah, she is crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.30,0:55:04.76,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,那孩子从生物学上讲 绝不可能是我的 行吗?\N{\rEng}It's a biological impossibility that that kid is mine, okay?
