Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.81,0:55:08.60,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,那你的子弹肯定是哑的\N{\rEng}So you must be shooting blanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.60,0:55:12.31,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你知道什么叫憋尿吗 沃利? 不知道?\N{\rEng}Do you know what continence is, Wally? No?
