Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.69,0:55:16.94,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,憋住 默数到十个数\N{\rEng}I hold my urine in, and I count to ten Mississippi.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.94,0:55:18.19,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,锻炼肌肉就得靠这个\N{\rEng}That's how you build up the muscle.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.19,0:55:19.61,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你那是他妈的找膀胱炎呢\N{\rEng}That's how you get a fuckin' bladder infection.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.61,0:55:21.70,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你干嘛呢? 那是我的信\N{\rEng}What are you doing? That's my mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.70,0:55:22.95,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗?\N{\rEng}Are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.74,0:55:25.28,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你得去买那些该死的尿布\N{\rEng}You need to grab them goddamn diapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.28,0:55:26.37,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不去\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.37,0:55:27.70,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,给我清醒点\N{\rEng}And get a fucking grip.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.70,0:55:29.25,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我才不当什么爹\N{\rEng}I'm not a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.14,0:55:48.52,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 哟 马蒂 - 怎么?\N{\rEng}- Yo, Marty. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.39,0:55:50.47,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,丽兹酒店是哪出?\N{\rEng}What's the Ritz?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.48,0:55:51.56,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,干嘛?\N{\rEng}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.56,0:55:54.02,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你收到一张1500美元的罚单\N{\rEng}You got a $1,500 fine
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.02,0:55:56.15,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,国际乒联发来的...\N{\rEng}from the International Table Tennis...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.15,0:55:57.77,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 啥? - ...说是协会要...\N{\rEng}- What? - ...Association and...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.77,0:55:59.86,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 还要... - 拿进来给我!\N{\rEng}- And they... - Bring it in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.86,0:56:01.24,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 还要把你这弱鸡给禁赛了 - 拿给我\N{\rEng}- And they banned your scrawny ass. - Give me that.
