Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.42,0:56:21.21,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,快点! 从那破浴缸里滚出来帮帮我!\N{\rEng}Come on! Get outta that fuckin' tub and help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.22,0:56:24.05,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我的狗快淹死了 伙计 快啊! 帮帮我!\N{\rEng}My dog's drowning, man. Come on! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.05,0:56:26.59,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,行 我把它翻过来 把手抽出来\N{\rEng}Okay, I'm flipping it. Take your arm out.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.60,0:56:28.10,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 一 二 - 把它抬开!\N{\rEng}- One. Two. - Lift it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.10,0:56:29.81,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,三\N{\rEng}Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.77,0:56:35.23,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,快把手抽出来! 噢我的天! 我的天!\N{\rEng}Take your arm out! Oh, my God! Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.81,0:56:36.94,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,操! 操!\N{\rEng}Fuck! Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.94,0:56:38.36,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,噢 妈的 你的手\N{\rEng}Oh, fuck, your arm.
