Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.16,0:56:48.57,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,别管那狗了! 手给我\N{\rEng}Don't worry about the dog! Give me your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.58,0:56:49.83,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 摩西 - 别乱动 别乱动\N{\rEng}- Moses. - Do nothing. Do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.83,0:56:51.29,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,有我在呢 别担心\N{\rEng}I got you. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.29,0:56:53.12,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,沃利 快叫救护车!\N{\rEng}Wally, call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.29,0:56:57.54,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你还好吧? - 不 我一点也不好\N{\rEng}- Are you good? - No, I'm not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.54,0:56:58.63,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我的眼镜呢?\N{\rEng}Where are my glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.63,0:57:00.50,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我是问你伤着没? 你刚把地板砸穿了\N{\rEng}I mean, are you hurt? You just fell through the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.50,0:57:02.67,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,真他妈扯淡 我得把钱要回来\N{\rEng}Fucking horseshit. I'm getting our money back.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.67,0:57:04.47,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,把钱要回来?\N{\rEng}Getting our money back?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.47,0:57:07.30,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,马蒂 咱们得赶紧溜 这才两块五毛钱 你在说啥呢?\N{\rEng}Marty, we gotta get the fuck out of here. It's $2.50. What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.30,0:57:09.30,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我要回来的可不止两块五 你没见刚才发生了什么?\N{\rEng}I'm asking for way more than $2.50. You see what just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.52,0:57:12.68,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,在这等着 等着\N{\rEng}Wait here. Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.56,0:57:15.43,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 等多久? - 十秒钟\N{\rEng}- For how long? - Ten seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.44,0:57:16.98,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我的鞋 我的衣服\N{\rEng}My shoes, my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.52,0:57:20.48,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,全湿透了 里面乱成一团\N{\rEng}Everything's soaking wet. It's a mess in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.69,0:57:24.28,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你给我闭嘴吧 - 你想练练?\N{\rEng}- Why don't you put a sock in it? - You wanna switch?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.28,0:57:27.24,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你! 我... 我早说了别用他妈的喷淋\N{\rEng}You! I... I told you not to use the fucking shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.24,0:57:29.82,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你才没说 是你把房租给我的 懂吗?\N{\rEng}No, you didn't. You're the one that rented me the room, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.83,0:57:31.16,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我从天花板掉下来差点摔断脖子\N{\rEng}I could have broken my neck falling out of that ceiling.
