Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.30,0:57:45.80,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 七块五! - 你什么也别想拿\N{\rEng}- $7.50! - You'll get nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.34,0:57:47.59,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 快点 帮帮我! - 医护人员来了\N{\rEng}- Come on. Help me! - Paramedics.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.59,0:57:49.05,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 好了 你们可来了 - 病人在哪儿?\N{\rEng}- Good, you're here. - Where's the patient at?
