Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.44,0:58:07.53,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,听着 把两块五还我 我就走 七块五不要了\N{\rEng}Listen, now. Just give me the $2.50, and I'll get outta here. Forget the $7.50.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.53,0:58:08.86,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 把两块五给我就行 - 我帮不了你\N{\rEng}- Just give me $2.50. - I can't help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.86,0:58:10.03,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,明天找老板去\N{\rEng}See the owner tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.03,0:58:11.12,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 小子 - 都是因为这破旅馆的烂天花板\N{\rEng}- Kid. - It's your shitty ceiling
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.12,0:58:13.08,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 给闹的 - 小子 噢!\N{\rEng}- in this crummy hotel. - Kid. Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.08,0:58:14.16,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我什么都不会给你 - 什么?\N{\rEng}- I ain't giving you nothing. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.16,0:58:16.66,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,小子 拜托 把狗送去兽医那儿\N{\rEng}Kid. Come on. Just bring the dog to the vet.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.66,0:58:18.46,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不行 我得工作 有活要干\N{\rEng}I can't. I got work. I got a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.46,0:58:19.58,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我不能被开除 - 你有工作?\N{\rEng}- I can't get fired. - You got a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.58,0:58:21.75,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我出双倍工钱 - 不 行不通 不行\N{\rEng}- I'll give you double what you're getting. - No, I can't. I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.75,0:58:23.96,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我给三倍 来吧\N{\rEng}I'll give you triple. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.96,0:58:25.42,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 悠着点 冷静下 - 行吧\N{\rEng}- Take it easy. Calm down. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.42,0:58:28.59,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,行 翻下那个包 看到椅子上的包了吗?\N{\rEng}Okay, look in that bag. See the bag on the chair?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.59,0:58:31.55,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,对 翻那个包 把它打开\N{\rEng}Yeah, go in that bag, okay? Open it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.55,0:58:33.14,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我得给你上个止血带\N{\rEng}I'm gonna apply a tourniquet to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.14,0:58:34.97,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我这就把原来那个撤了\N{\rEng}I'm gonna remove the other tourniquet right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.97,0:58:37.10,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,拿五十给你自己 没错\N{\rEng}Take 50 for yourself. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.10,0:58:38.31,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,再带五十给兽医 明白吗?\N{\rEng}Bring 50 for the vet, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.31,0:58:39.56,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,血都喷出来了\N{\rEng}We got blood squirting out.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.56,0:58:41.10,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他在13街和1大道交口\N{\rEng}He's on 13th and 1st.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.10,0:58:43.77,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,告诉他我一完事就赶过去 懂吗?\N{\rEng}And tell him I'll be there as soon as I can get there, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.77,0:58:45.82,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你居然要给这混蛋钱?\N{\rEng}You're gonna give this motherfucker money?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.82,0:58:47.65,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,是他他妈让浴缸砸到你身上的\N{\rEng}He's the one who fuckin' dropped the tub on ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.65,0:58:49.36,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我警告过他别进那个破浴缸的\N{\rEng}I told him not to get in the fuckin' bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.36,0:58:50.91,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,真他妈讲究 小子\N{\rEng}Fucking mensch, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.91,0:58:52.57,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,担架准备好了吗? 咱们送他去贝尔维尤\N{\rEng}Stretcher ready? We'll take him to Bellevue.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.57,0:58:54.66,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,真他妈讲究\N{\rEng}Fucking mensch.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.66,0:58:55.99,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,咱们现在掉头还来得及\N{\rEng}We can still turn around
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.99,0:58:57.83,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 能送他去兽医那儿 - 不行 不行\N{\rEng}- and take him to the vet. - No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.83,0:58:59.91,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 五十块钱绰绰有余了 - 知道什么比五十块更好吗? 一百块\N{\rEng}- Fifty dollars is more than enough. - You know what's better than 50? 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.92,0:59:01.37,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,有一百块本钱 咱们能赢个盆满钵满\N{\rEng}We can clean house with a hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.38,0:59:03.00,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,别贪得无厌了 你这该死的犹太佬\N{\rEng}Don't be greedy, you fucking Jew.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.00,0:59:05.92,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不 不 是1500美元的罚款 是你拿给我看的\N{\rEng}No, no. It's a $1,500 fine. You're the one that showed it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.92,0:59:08.09,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,顺便说下 咱们得连续两周每晚都这么干\N{\rEng}By the way, we gotta do this every night for two weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.09,0:59:09.67,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 否则我就去不了日本了 - "咱们"? 噢 不不不\N{\rEng}- or else I can't go to Japan. - "We"? Oh, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.68,0:59:11.97,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我可不想因为你捅了娄子就两周不去上班\N{\rEng}I'm not taking two weeks off work 'cause you fucked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.97,0:59:13.05,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿 拿着这个 伙计\N{\rEng}Hey. Take this, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.05,0:59:15.68,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,拿着 没错 好孩子\N{\rEng}Take this. There you go. Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.68,0:59:18.35,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,把这混蛋的项圈松一松 伙计\N{\rEng}Loosen up the collar on this motherfucker, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.35,0:59:20.18,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 行了 - 他听着像个破暖气片\N{\rEng}- All right. - He sound like a radiator.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.19,0:59:21.27,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,咱们先去打球\N{\rEng}We're gonna go play,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.27,0:59:22.77,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,回来的路上再送他去兽医那儿\N{\rEng}we'll drop him off at the vet on the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.77,0:59:25.94,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 耽搁两小时对他算得了什么? - 马蒂 我都约好车了 伙计\N{\rEng}- What's a couple of hours to this guy? - Marty, I got rides set up, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.94,0:59:27.78,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,唉 摩西\N{\rEng}Huh. Moses.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.79,0:59:47.63,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,三号球道 归你了\N{\rEng}Lane three. That's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.76,0:59:56.55,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 怎么样? - 有什么能帮您的?\N{\rEng}- Hi, how you doing? - Could I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.56,0:59:57.81,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,能给我开个球道吗?\N{\rEng}Can I get a lane?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.52,1:00:01.52,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,大概得等半小时 四十分钟\N{\rEng}Probably gonna be a half hour, 40 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.52,1:00:02.69,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 没问题 - 你确定能等?\N{\rEng}- That's okay. - You all right with that?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.69,1:00:04.73,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 要租鞋吗? - 我待会儿再拿\N{\rEng}- You want shoes? - I'll just grab 'em later.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.37,1:00:16.58,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,搞定 结束\N{\rEng}Done. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.37,1:00:19.24,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,弱得可怜 给钱\N{\rEng}Fucking pathetic. Pay up.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.24,1:00:20.45,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,谁想打下一局?\N{\rEng}Who wants next?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.45,1:00:22.46,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我能打吗? 嘿! 我能来一局吗?\N{\rEng}Can I play? Hey! Can I play?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.46,1:00:24.25,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 一块钱一局 - 行吧\N{\rEng}- It's a dollar a game. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.25,1:00:25.96,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你叫什么? - 塞思\N{\rEng}- What's your name? - Seth.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.96,1:00:27.67,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,来几个对攻热热身吧\N{\rEng}Let's get a warm-up rally going.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.67,1:00:29.42,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不 要打就掏钱 否则闭嘴 我不打白工\N{\rEng}Nah. Put up or shut up. I don't play for free.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.17,1:00:31.59,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,行吧 没听过这规矩\N{\rEng}All right. Never heard of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.59,1:00:32.88,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我押钱 - 他管账\N{\rEng}- I'm holding. - He's holding.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.88,1:00:34.05,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你管账? 凭什么是他管?\N{\rEng}You're holding? Why is he holding?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.05,1:00:36.09,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你带钱了吗? - 我能信任你吗?\N{\rEng}- Have you got yours? - Can I trust you?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.09,1:00:37.47,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,信任我 绝对没问题\N{\rEng}Trust me, you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.76,1:00:40.97,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 战况如何? - 好了 塞思对阵罗杰\N{\rEng}- Where are we at? - All right, Seth vs. Roger.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.97,1:00:41.98,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,一块钱一局\N{\rEng}Dollar game.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.64,1:00:43.94,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我发球\N{\rEng}I serve.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.94,1:00:45.52,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你干嘛呢? 我看都没看\N{\rEng}What are you doing? I'm not even looking.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.52,1:00:47.77,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 1比0 - 我刚才看都没看\N{\rEng}- One-zip. - I wasn't even looking.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.40,1:00:54.90,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 你不能那么干 - 啥?\N{\rEng}- No, you can't do that. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.91,1:00:56.45,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你得让球落到对面\N{\rEng}You gotta let the ball hit the other side.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.45,1:00:57.74,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你不能用球拍接球 我得分\N{\rEng}You can't catch it with your paddle. My point.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.74,1:00:59.20,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你说什么呢? - 你不能那么干\N{\rEng}- What are you talking about? - You can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.20,1:01:00.74,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你得让球掉下桌子才行\N{\rEng}You gotta let the ball fall off the table.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.74,1:01:02.29,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 荒谬至极 - 你在耍赖\N{\rEng}- That's ridiculous. - You're cheating.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.29,1:01:04.08,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我耍赖? - 对 这就叫耍赖\N{\rEng}- I'm cheating? - Yeah, that's called cheating.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.08,1:01:06.37,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你没守规矩 - 行吧 分给你\N{\rEng}- You're not following the rules. - Fine. Take the point.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.38,1:01:07.92,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,谢谢 把球给我 1比1\N{\rEng}- Thank you. Give me the ball. - One-one.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.92,1:01:08.92,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,操\N{\rEng}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.21,1:01:12.63,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,好险 打得好 打得好\N{\rEng}- That was close. - That was good. That was good.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.63,1:01:14.34,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,噢 不不不不不\N{\rEng}Oh. No, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.34,1:01:15.51,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不不 拿走吧\N{\rEng}No, no. Take it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.51,1:01:17.72,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我本该让你五分的 伙计\N{\rEng}I should have spotted you, like, five points, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.72,1:01:20.14,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你今天够倒霉了 留着吧\N{\rEng}You've had a rough enough day already. Keep it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.14,1:01:21.47,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,谢谢 兄弟 谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you, brother. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.47,1:01:22.85,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,没事儿\N{\rEng}It's all good.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.85,1:01:24.10,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,打得不错\N{\rEng}Good game.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.10,1:01:26.06,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,好了 亚当 亚当 走着\N{\rEng}All right, Adam. Adam, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.36,1:01:30.69,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你想押多少? 我能出五毛\N{\rEng}- What do you want to put on? - I can go 50 cents.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.69,1:01:31.82,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你有球吗?\N{\rEng}You got a ball?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.82,1:01:33.15,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你的鼻子怎么了?\N{\rEng}What happened to your nose?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.15,1:01:34.53,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我有球 我有球\N{\rEng}I got one, I got one.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.53,1:01:36.40,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,有个乘客赖账跑了\N{\rEng}Fare ran out on me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.41,1:01:38.61,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,赖什么账? 发生什么了?\N{\rEng}Fare from what? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.62,1:01:41.20,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我是个计程车司机 曼哈顿来的\N{\rEng}I'm a taxi driver. From Manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.91,1:01:43.20,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,曼哈顿? 昂\N{\rEng}- Manhattan? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.20,1:01:44.75,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,那路费可不便宜 伙计\N{\rEng}That's an expensive trip, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.75,1:01:46.62,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,噢 可不是 二十 二十五块钱呢\N{\rEng}Oh, yeah. $20, $25.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.62,1:01:48.67,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,碰上有钱的主儿能给五块小费\N{\rEng}Well, the high rollers tip five,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.67,1:01:51.00,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,那就是五块小费 而且...\N{\rEng}so that's five in tips. And...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.00,1:01:54.09,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我他妈刚送到地方 那家伙就勒住我\N{\rEng}I fucking get to the spot, the guy chokes me out,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.09,1:01:55.84,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,对着我后脑勺一顿猛拳 - 不会吧\N{\rEng}- punching me in the back of the head. - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.84,1:01:58.34,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,抢了我的钱拔腿就跑\N{\rEng}Takes my money and run the fuck off.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.34,1:02:00.80,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,后来我追上那混蛋 嘿 结果...\N{\rEng}Caught up to the motherfucker, and, boy...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.80,1:02:04.35,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我把他揍得眼冒金星 伙计\N{\rEng}I beat the brights off that motherfucker, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.18,1:02:06.73,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,然后我搜了他全身\N{\rEng}And I took what he had.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.73,1:02:07.98,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你把他搜刮了?\N{\rEng}You took what he had?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.98,1:02:09.40,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,那当然! 你他妈说对了\N{\rEng}Hell, yeah! You fucking damn right.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.40,1:02:10.86,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你把那钱加进你的那叠钞票里了? 当然了\N{\rEng}- You added that to your roll? - Sure did.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.86,1:02:12.15,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,就在我刚才看你掏出的那厚厚一叠里\N{\rEng}To that fat roll I've seen you pulling out.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.15,1:02:13.65,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这是原则 问题在于他妈的原则\N{\rEng}It's principle. It's fucking principle!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.65,1:02:15.32,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我懂 我要是你就把它藏好\N{\rEng}I understand that. I would keep it hidden.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.32,1:02:18.28,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,在这儿这种地方 最好别露白\N{\rEng}I would keep that down, if I were you, in this place.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.28,1:02:21.07,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我告诉你 可不是谁都像克里斯蒂安这么面善\N{\rEng}Not everybody's as nice as Christian is, I'm telling you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.07,1:02:22.45,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这就是我想说的\N{\rEng}That's my point.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.45,1:02:24.33,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,那在那儿坐着的混蛋又是谁?\N{\rEng}What about that asshole right there?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.33,1:02:26.16,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我哪他妈知道那是谁\N{\rEng}I don't know who the fuck that guy is.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.16,1:02:28.08,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你不能那样发球 怎么不能?\N{\rEng}- You can't serve like that. - What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.08,1:02:29.29,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我这么发球都好几年了\N{\rEng}I've been serving like that for years.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.29,1:02:31.96,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿 罗杰 罗杰 嘿 太荒谬了\N{\rEng}- Hey, Roger. Roger. Hello. - That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.96,1:02:33.63,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,再给我一分钟 我们的球道空出来了\N{\rEng}- Give me one more minute. - Our lane is open.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.63,1:02:35.84,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,球道能等 没事儿 不行 咱们得马上走\N{\rEng}- The lane can wait. It's fine. - No, we gotta go now.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.84,1:02:37.67,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,人家要让给别人了 我正打球呢\N{\rEng}- They're gonna give it away. - I'm playing now.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.67,1:02:40.89,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我为了打保龄球等了一晚上 赶紧的 走啊\N{\rEng}I have been waiting all night to bowl. Let's go. Come on.
