Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.84,1:07:24.00,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 凭什么要我... - 滚出来!\N{\rEng}- Why I gotta be-- - Get the fuck out!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.10,1:07:36.31,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,操!\N{\rEng}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.31,1:07:39.02,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 马蒂 快他妈走! - 操你大爷!\N{\rEng}- Marty, let's fucking go! - Fuck yourself!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.10,1:07:42.02,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,走 走 走 走 快走\N{\rEng}Go, go, go, go, go.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.77,1:07:44.27,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,沃利 留神! 留神! 电线杆!\N{\rEng}Wally, watch out! Watch out! The pole!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.36,1:07:46.86,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不! 不!\N{\rEng}No! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.86,1:07:48.69,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,沃利 狗 狗还在那 沃利\N{\rEng}Wally, the dog. The dog, Wally.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.69,1:07:50.74,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 去他妈的狗! - 我得带着狗!\N{\rEng}- Fuck that dog! - I need the dog!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.74,1:07:51.82,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,去他妈的狗\N{\rEng}Fuck the dog,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.82,1:07:54.53,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 也去你的 伙计! 去你的!\N{\rEng}- and fuck you, man! Fuck you, man! - Oh, no. No!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.12,1:07:56.66,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他们会扣我工资的!\N{\rEng}They'll take this out of my paycheck!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.66,1:08:00.71,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我车废了 伙计! 我他妈要丢工作了!\N{\rEng}My car's fucked up, man! I'm gonna lose my fucking job!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.71,1:08:03.50,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这是我的全部! 我还有人要养呢!\N{\rEng}This is all I got! I got people depending on me!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.50,1:08:06.00,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我有一大堆责任要担! - 我也有责任\N{\rEng}- I got real responsibilities! - I got responsibilities too.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.00,1:08:07.50,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你屁个责任! - 你他妈觉得...\N{\rEng}- No, you don't! - What the fuck you think--
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.13,1:08:14.26,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ ...可能再次消融 ♪\N{\rEng}♪ ...may melt again ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.26,1:08:19.06,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 像那冬雪一般消融 ♪\N{\rEng}♪ Like winter snow That melts ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.06,1:08:20.60,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 伴随 ♪\N{\rEng}♪ With ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.60,1:08:23.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 四月的细雨 ♪\N{\rEng}♪ April rain ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.40,1:08:27.19,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 亲爱的 在我心底 ♪\N{\rEng}♪ For darling, in my heart ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.69,1:08:31.82,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 你将永远常驻 ♪\N{\rEng}♪ You always will remain ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.36,1:08:39.12,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,♪ 随着夏去秋来 ♪\N{\rEng}♪ As summer turns to fall ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.58,1:08:43.50,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,多谢了 谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you so much. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.50,1:08:44.79,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我会补偿你的 好吗?\N{\rEng}I'm gonna make it up to you. All right?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.79,1:08:46.92,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,别生我气 行吗?\N{\rEng}Don't be mad at me. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.92,1:08:48.79,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我会给你买辆新出租的 真的\N{\rEng}I'm gonna get you a new cab. All right?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.80,1:08:50.59,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,别担心 沃利 我爱你\N{\rEng}Don't worry about it. Wally, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.59,1:08:51.84,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,帮我关个门\N{\rEng}Close my door.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.99,1:09:18.99,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿 马蒂\N{\rEng}Hey, Marty.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.26,1:09:33.97,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 泰德 - 嘿 马蒂 伙计 近来可好?\N{\rEng}- Hey, Ted. - Hey, Marty. How you doing, man?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.97,1:09:35.26,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 劳伦斯在吗? - 节哀顺变\N{\rEng}- Is Lawrence here? - Sorry about your loss.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.26,1:09:36.93,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,没事的 劳伦斯今晚在这儿吗?\N{\rEng}It's all right. Is Lawrence here tonight?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.93,1:09:38.72,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,昂 在 就在这附近哪个地儿\N{\rEng}Uh, yeah. He's around here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.72,1:09:40.64,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 好的 知道了 谢了 - 行 行\N{\rEng}- Okay. All right. Thank you. - Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.64,1:09:41.85,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 见到你很高兴 伙计 - 嗯\N{\rEng}- Good to see you, man. - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.35,1:09:48.52,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 最近怎么样? - 马蒂\N{\rEng}- How you been? - Marty.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.52,1:09:50.40,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 见到你真好 - 嘿 马蒂\N{\rEng}- Nice to see you. - Hello, Marty.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.40,1:09:52.07,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿 今晚能借住你的后屋吗 求你了?\N{\rEng}Hey, can I stay in your back room tonight, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.07,1:09:55.24,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿 你的小妞在后头呢 知道吗?\N{\rEng}Hey, hey. Got your girl in the back, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.24,1:09:56.99,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,她怀孕了 情绪特别糟\N{\rEng}She pregnant. She real upset.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.99,1:09:58.99,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,噢 天哪 好吧 知道了\N{\rEng}Oh, God. Okay. All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.99,1:10:00.49,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,额 我去跟她谈谈\N{\rEng}Uh, let me go talk to her,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.49,1:10:02.12,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,但在见我之前 麻烦千万别走开\N{\rEng}but then please don't leave without finding me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.12,1:10:03.91,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 放心 我就在这儿 - 好 很高兴见到你\N{\rEng}- Yeah, I'll be here. Okay. - All right. Nice to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.91,1:10:05.33,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 好的 很高兴见到你 - 嗯\N{\rEng}- All right, good to see you. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.72,1:10:22.06,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿 你怎么在这儿?\N{\rEng}Hey. What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.02,1:10:24.68,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我没想打扰你 我知道你很忙\N{\rEng}I don't mean to bother you. I know you're really busy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.68,1:10:27.31,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你脸是怎么搞的? - 我真的没别的地方去了\N{\rEng}- What the hell happened to your face? - I didn't really have anywhere else to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.31,1:10:28.48,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 让我看看 - 他突然就开始...\N{\rEng}- Let me see. - He just started...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.48,1:10:29.98,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他突然就开始对我吼\N{\rEng}he just started yelling at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.98,1:10:32.23,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他疯了一样 还扯我的衣服\N{\rEng}And he was really mad and he was ripping my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.23,1:10:34.82,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 他把你弄成这样的? - 他真的吓死我了\N{\rEng}- He did this to you? - He was really scaring me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.82,1:10:36.57,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我只是不知道还能去哪儿\N{\rEng}I just didn't know where else to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.95,1:10:39.20,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你在生我的气吗?\N{\rEng}Are you mad at me?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.30,1:11:41.59,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,瑞秋?\N{\rEng}Rachel?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.59,1:11:44.10,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不 不是瑞秋 是马蒂 开门\N{\rEng}No, it's not Rachel. It's Marty. Open the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.91,1:12:06.70,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿 迪昂 怎么样 伙计? 真的很感谢\N{\rEng}Hey, Dion. How you doing, man? I really appreciate this.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.70,1:12:08.20,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,顺便说下 这是我妹妹瑞秋\N{\rEng}This is my sister Rachel, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.20,1:12:10.37,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,瑞秋 这是我哥们 也是生意伙伴 迪昂\N{\rEng}Rachel, this is my buddy, my business partner, Dion.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.37,1:12:11.62,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 - 嘿\N{\rEng}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.62,1:12:12.96,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,她那儿淹水了\N{\rEng}Her place flooded.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.96,1:12:15.17,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,她得在这儿凑合一晚 没问题吧?\N{\rEng}She needs a place to crash for the night. That's okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.17,1:12:16.25,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我不确定 伙计 这...\N{\rEng}I don't know, man, it's...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.25,1:12:19.26,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我知道 但我不能让她待在有霉菌孢子什么的破地儿\N{\rEng}I know, but I can't have her exposed to mold and spores and shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.26,1:12:22.47,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,迪 拜托 她都怀孕八个月了 懂吗?\N{\rEng}D, come on, she's eight months pregnant, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.47,1:12:23.72,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,拜托...\N{\rEng}Come on...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.72,1:12:25.14,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,那可是我亲外甥\N{\rEng}That's my nephew.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.14,1:12:26.64,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我不该带人回来的\N{\rEng}I'm not supposed to have people over.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.76,1:12:31.14,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,她家里情况很糟 我不能让她回去 求你了\N{\rEng}She's got a bad situation at home. I can't have her going back there. Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.14,1:12:32.73,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,行吧 进来吧 你可以住一晚\N{\rEng}All right. Come on. You can spend the night.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.73,1:12:35.19,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,但明天我爸妈回来前你得离开\N{\rEng}You just gotta be out of here by tomorrow before my parents get back.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.19,1:12:36.27,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,没问题\N{\rEng}Okay. No problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.27,1:12:38.02,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,咱们得趁聚在一起把时间利用好\N{\rEng}We should take advantage of the time we have together.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.03,1:12:39.53,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,好好敲定咱们的业务计划\N{\rEng}You know, really firm up our business plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.53,1:12:41.86,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这样你爸回来就能看到咱们有多专业了\N{\rEng}That way, when your dad gets back, he sees how organized we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.86,1:12:43.20,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,是啊 他现在挺火大的\N{\rEng}Yeah, he's pretty upset.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.20,1:12:44.95,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你把这堆库存丢给咱们八个月没管\N{\rEng}You left us with all of this inventory for eight months.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.95,1:12:46.99,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,没关系 几周后我拿下冠军\N{\rEng}That's fine. In a few weeks I'll take the championship.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.99,1:12:48.08,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,咱们就能重回正轨\N{\rEng}We'll be right back on track.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.08,1:12:49.83,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 球就在这儿 - 真的? 哪呢?\N{\rEng}- Balls are right in here. - Really? Where?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.83,1:12:51.00,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,最上面的箱子\N{\rEng}The top box.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.50,1:12:52.50,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,谢了\N{\rEng}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.63,1:13:01.01,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 哇 你做了橙色的?\N{\rEng}- Whoa. You did the orange? - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.01,1:13:02.09,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你怎么做成橙色的?\N{\rEng}How'd you do the orange?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.09,1:13:03.67,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我联系了海力士的人\N{\rEng}I contacted someone at Halex.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.68,1:13:05.22,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他们帮我给赛璐珞上了色\N{\rEng}They colored the celluloid for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.22,1:13:06.93,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 怎么搞定的? - 靠钱呗 宝贝\N{\rEng}- How? - Money, baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.72,1:13:09.39,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我和我老爸都看好你\N{\rEng}Me and my pop, we believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.39,1:13:11.14,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我们投了钱的 这就是他一直火大的原因\N{\rEng}We're invested. That's why he's been so mad.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.98,1:13:14.64,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧这个 瑞秋\N{\rEng}Check it out, Rachel.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.65,1:13:15.90,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,来 看看这包装\N{\rEng}Here, check out the packaging.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.73,1:13:21.44,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,"马蒂至尊 马蒂·毛瑟锦标赛官方乒乓球\N{\rEng}"Marty Supreme. The official Marty Mauser championship table tennis ball.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.44,1:13:22.69,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,专业制造 橙色..."\N{\rEng}Professionally made. Orange..."
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.69,1:13:24.57,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,橙色球体? 你想出来的?\N{\rEng}Orange spheres? You came up with that?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.57,1:13:25.70,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,是啊 挺棒的吧?\N{\rEng}Yeah. Pretty good, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.70,1:13:28.49,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,何止棒啊 迪昂 这... 我惊呆了\N{\rEng}Pretty good? Dion, this is... I'm stunned.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.95,1:13:30.08,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,太震撼了\N{\rEng}I'm stunned.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.08,1:13:32.04,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 还是手绘的 - 你画的?\N{\rEng}- Hand-drawn too. - You drew this?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.04,1:13:33.45,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 对 - 真是神来之笔\N{\rEng}- Yeah. - It's inspired.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.46,1:13:34.54,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,多谢夸奖\N{\rEng}I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.54,1:13:36.46,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你都不知道自己多有能耐\N{\rEng}I don't think you know what you're capable of.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.46,1:13:37.83,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你看 - 真的多谢\N{\rEng}- Check it out. - Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.84,1:13:39.09,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,哇\N{\rEng}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.09,1:13:40.96,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,真的很漂亮\N{\rEng}it's really nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.67,1:13:44.59,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 这是你的房间? - 不是 是我弟弟的\N{\rEng}- This is your room? - No, it's my brother's.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.59,1:13:46.13,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你还有弟弟? 你从来没跟我说过\N{\rEng}You have a brother? You never told me you had a brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.13,1:13:47.80,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,是个亲弟弟 已经搬走了\N{\rEng}It's a younger brother. He moved out.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.80,1:13:48.80,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,那他房间空着?\N{\rEng}So his room is free?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.22,1:13:50.68,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 额 对 - 我先去安顿一下我妹\N{\rEng}- Uh, yeah. - Let me get my sister situated.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.68,1:13:52.14,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 五分钟后去找你 - 行\N{\rEng}- I'll come find you in five minutes. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.14,1:13:53.14,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,五分钟\N{\rEng}Five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.39,1:13:55.89,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,迪昂 你真让我刮目相看\N{\rEng}I'm really impressed, D.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.89,1:13:57.31,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢 - 说真的\N{\rEng}- Thank you. - Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.23,1:13:59.52,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,真是个特别的人\N{\rEng}Special guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.52,1:14:01.53,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我把床给你弄舒服点 好吗?\N{\rEng}Let me get the bed comfortable for you, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.99,1:14:04.28,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,那你现在要出去吗?\N{\rEng}So are you gonna go out there now?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.28,1:14:06.36,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,对 我得琢磨下明天的计划\N{\rEng}Yeah, I gotta figure my plan out for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.36,1:14:07.61,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,为什么? 什么计划?\N{\rEng}Why? Plan for what?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.61,1:14:09.95,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我得理理头绪\N{\rEng}Well, I need to get my head together.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.62,1:14:12.12,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,怎么说?\N{\rEng}How so?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.12,1:14:15.37,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,有个有钱佬找我干活 我打算联系他\N{\rEng}This rich guy hit me up for a job. I think I'm gonna get in touch with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.87,1:14:18.04,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 真的? - 是啊\N{\rEng}- Really? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.04,1:14:20.59,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 干什么活? 什么工作? - 不重要 能去日本就行\N{\rEng}- A job for what? What job? - It doesn't matter. Just to get to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.13,1:14:22.67,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 为了锦标赛? - 对\N{\rEng}- For the championship? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.17,1:14:24.17,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,哇\N{\rEng}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.92,1:14:28.09,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,虽然生活一团糟 但我会搞定的\N{\rEng}Everything in my life is falling apart, but I'm gonna figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.09,1:14:29.89,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,需要帮忙吗? 我可以帮你\N{\rEng}Do you need any help? I could help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.89,1:14:31.80,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 没事 不用了 - 我能做点什么吗?\N{\rEng}- No, it's all right. It's all right. - Can I do anything?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.81,1:14:33.10,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你饿吗?\N{\rEng}Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.10,1:14:34.81,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 不饿 - 确定?\N{\rEng}- No. - You sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.81,1:14:37.06,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,额 我去另一个房间待着 行吗?\N{\rEng}Uh, I'll just be in the other room, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.40,1:14:42.86,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 迪昂 我从没见过这种球 - 我就说吧 伙计\N{\rEng}- Dion, I've never seen anything like this. - I told you, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.86,1:14:44.32,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,伙计 咱们得好好叙叙旧\N{\rEng}Man, we have to have a big catch-up
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.32,1:14:47.32,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,因为这是八个月来发生在我身上最伟大的事\N{\rEng}'cause this is the greatest thing that's happened to me in the last eight months.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.32,1:14:48.91,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,谁能想到呢? 海力士?\N{\rEng}Who would've thought? Halex?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.46,1:15:03.29,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,早上好 洛克威尔油墨公司\N{\rEng}Good morning. Rockwell Ink.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.30,1:15:05.76,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,是的 你好 请帮我接米尔顿·洛克威尔先生\N{\rEng}Yes, hi, can I speak to Milton Rockwell, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.76,1:15:07.84,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,他现在不在 需要留个言吗?\N{\rEng}He's not in at the moment. Can I take a message?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.84,1:15:09.13,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,好吧 什么时候能联系到他?\N{\rEng}Okay, when are you expecting him?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.13,1:15:11.09,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,额 他今天在外面办公\N{\rEng}Well, he's working off-site today.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.09,1:15:12.93,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 再问一遍 需要留言吗? - 趁热喝\N{\rEng}- Again, can I take a message?- It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.93,1:15:14.26,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,太感谢了\N{\rEng}Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.26,1:15:16.18,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,等我妹醒了 能给她也弄点吗?\N{\rEng}Can you make some for my sister for when she wakes up?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.18,1:15:17.77,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 她会很饿的 - 喂?\N{\rEng}- She'll be really hungry. - Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.77,1:15:19.19,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你说他在外面哪儿?\N{\rEng}You said off-site where?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.19,1:15:21.02,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我不能告诉你相关信息\N{\rEng}I'm sorry, I can't give you that information.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.02,1:15:22.94,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 您到底要不要留言? - 要\N{\rEng}- Would you like to leave a message or not?- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.94,1:15:25.44,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,能替我向他道个歉吗?\N{\rEng}Can you apologize to him on my behalf?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.44,1:15:27.44,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我是原本今早要和他\N{\rEng}I was the young gentleman that was supposed to have breakfast
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.44,1:15:28.53,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,一起吃早餐的那个年轻人\N{\rEng}with him this morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.53,1:15:30.91,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我不清楚 - 就是他儿子那个营的\N{\rEng}- I'm not familiar.- From his son's battalion.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.91,1:15:33.78,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我对此一无所知\N{\rEng}I'm sorry, I-- I don't know anything about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.78,1:15:36.70,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,我这儿有他儿子的个人遗物 应该交给他\N{\rEng}I have some personal belongings of his son's I was supposed to give to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.70,1:15:39.79,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,信件 纪念品之类的 但我搞砸了 睡过头了\N{\rEng}Letters and mementos and such, but I messed up and I overslept.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.79,1:15:42.75,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,我今天就要离开这儿 要不邮寄给他更方便?\N{\rEng}I'm leaving town today, but I could mail it to him if that's easier.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.75,1:15:44.44,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 不 不行 - 不行? 好的\N{\rEng}- No, no, no.- No? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.84,1:15:49.01,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,这样吧 你试试往莫罗斯科剧院打个电话\N{\rEng}How about this, why don't you try giving a call over to the Morosco Theatre.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.51,1:15:50.88,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,莫罗斯科剧院\N{\rEng}The Morosco Theatre.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.88,1:15:53.47,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,所以我算什么? 我在干嘛?\N{\rEng}So, I'm like what? What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.47,1:15:54.89,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,跑这儿来毁了我的夜晚\N{\rEng}Coming up here to wreck my night.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.89,1:15:56.76,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,说真的 妈 我压根不知道你会来\N{\rEng}Honest, Mama, I didn't even know you were coming here.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.77,1:15:58.02,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我受够了你耍花招\N{\rEng}I'm through with you playing games.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.02,1:15:59.27,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我只是来找点乐子\N{\rEng}I was just coming for a good time.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.27,1:16:01.65,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我听说应召女郎都在这儿扎堆\N{\rEng}I heard this was where all the call girls gather.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.77,1:16:07.57,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我正努力重建生活 你不明白吗?\N{\rEng}I'm trying to rebuild my life here. Don't you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.57,1:16:09.82,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我看是把自己卖给出价最高的人吧\N{\rEng}More like selling out to the highest bidder.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.82,1:16:12.36,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你没资格评判我 杰德\N{\rEng}You've got no right to judge me, Jed.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.36,1:16:14.57,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我拼尽全力才换来那么一点幸福\N{\rEng}I fought tooth and nail for every shred of happiness
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.58,1:16:17.16,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 哪怕只有一点... - 对 那你给过我什么?\N{\rEng}- I've ever found while you... - Right, and what did you give to me?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.16,1:16:19.00,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你从没相信过我 一次都没有!\N{\rEng}You never believed in me. Not once!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.21,1:16:23.54,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你想沉溺于自怜吗? 杰德 烤箱在那儿呢!\N{\rEng}You wanna wallow in self-pity? Well, here's an oven, Jed!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.54,1:16:24.63,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,阿尔玛!\N{\rEng}Alma!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.63,1:16:25.71,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我没事 亨利\N{\rEng}I'm all right, Henry.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.71,1:16:28.05,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 请给我们留点私人时间 - 我妈就是个烂货\N{\rEng}- Just give us a minute, please. - My mama is a dirty bird.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.05,1:16:30.01,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嘴放干净点 杰迪代亚\N{\rEng}Be careful now, Jedidiah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.01,1:16:34.47,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你给她穿的那身华丽衣裳 只是掩盖她身上的臭味!\N{\rEng}And that fancy dress you put her in is the only thing keeping in the stench!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.60,1:16:38.85,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不许碰我孩子\N{\rEng}Don't you lay a hand on my child.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.85,1:16:40.56,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我... 抱歉 额...\N{\rEng}I-I'm sorry, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.27,1:16:47.73,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,妈 我做错什么了?\N{\rEng}Mama, what did I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.73,1:16:49.74,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,走! 快跑!\N{\rEng}Go! Run!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.12,1:16:58.78,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 门锁了 - 噢 我的天\N{\rEng}- The door is locked. - Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.79,1:17:00.16,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑!\N{\rEng}You've gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.16,1:17:02.46,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼 谁给这门加了插销?\N{\rEng}For Christ's sake, did somebody put a latch on the door?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.46,1:17:04.96,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 噢天呐 - 我以为刚才节奏挺好的\N{\rEng}- Oh, God. - I thought we had a good rhythm going.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.96,1:17:08.25,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,节奏挺好? 你住哪个星球啊 节奏算哪门子好\N{\rEng}A good rhythm going? On what planet is that a good rhythm
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.25,1:17:09.67,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 如果你就自个儿在那演? - 我入戏了\N{\rEng}- if you're alone in a room? - I was in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.67,1:17:12.34,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,搞得跟我不在场一样 入戏? 戏在哪呢?\N{\rEng}It's like I wasn't even there. In it? In what?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.34,1:17:16.26,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 格伦 我一句话都插不上 - 我懂 咱们会修正的\N{\rEng}- Glenn, I couldn't get a word out. - I understand. We're gonna fix it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.26,1:17:18.76,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 排练过程就是为了解决这些 - 真他妈绝了\N{\rEng}- That's what a rehearsal process is for. - Fuck's sake.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.76,1:17:20.85,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,先停一下吧 大家休息五分钟\N{\rEng}Let's lose this, by the way. Everybody take five.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.85,1:17:22.27,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,帮个忙 各位...\N{\rEng}Do me a favor, everybody...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.27,1:17:24.56,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,得有人跟他说说这事\N{\rEng}Somebody needs to tell him something.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.56,1:17:26.44,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 简直离谱 - 不可理喻\N{\rEng}- It's impossible. - Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.90,1:17:29.69,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 喝水吗? - 喝\N{\rEng}- Do you want some water? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.69,1:17:31.86,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我去给你拿点 - 天哪\N{\rEng}- Let me bring you some. - God.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.78,1:17:37.28,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿 凯\N{\rEng}Hey, Kay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.28,1:17:38.95,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿 是马蒂\N{\rEng}Hey, it's Marty.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.16,1:17:42.96,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,伦敦那个\N{\rEng}From London.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.46,1:17:45.54,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你怎么跑这儿来了?\N{\rEng}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.54,1:17:47.29,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,额 我有个舞台技师协会的朋友\N{\rEng}Well, I got a friend in the stagehands union.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.29,1:17:48.54,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我过来给他送点东西\N{\rEng}I was dropping something off for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.54,1:17:50.71,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你刚才看了? - 是的 希望没冒犯到你\N{\rEng}- You watched that? - Yeah, I hope that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.71,1:17:51.84,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,噢 天呐\N{\rEng}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.84,1:17:54.17,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿 没想到你又开始演戏了\N{\rEng}Hey, I can't believe you're acting again.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.17,1:17:56.34,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,那不叫演戏 他压根不让我演\N{\rEng}That wasn't acting. He won't let me act.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.34,1:17:59.01,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嗯 看得出来挺闹心的 那家伙什么来头?\N{\rEng}Yeah, no, that looked frustrating. What's the deal with that guy?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.01,1:18:00.35,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,别提了\N{\rEng}Don't get me started.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.35,1:18:02.06,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,是啊 你刚才演技完全吊打他\N{\rEng}Yeah, you were running circles around him.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.85,1:18:04.06,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,那是当然\N{\rEng}Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.06,1:18:05.69,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,确实 简直神了\N{\rEng}Yeah. It was unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.69,1:18:07.35,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他连续三天不睡觉\N{\rEng}He stays up for three days in a row
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.35,1:18:09.69,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,就因为他的角色应该很疲惫\N{\rEng}because his character is supposed to be tired.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.69,1:18:11.11,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 简直不可理喻 - 噢天呐\N{\rEng}- It's obnoxious. - Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.78,1:18:15.86,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,要是他真那么投入 为什么要停下来?\N{\rEng}If he's so committed, why'd he stop the scene?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.07,1:18:18.95,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他干嘛不一拳打穿那个帘子\N{\rEng}Why didn't he punch his hand through the screen,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.95,1:18:20.08,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,从里面把锁打开?\N{\rEng}unlock it from the other side?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.62,1:18:23.41,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 对吧? 换我会这么干 - 格伦!\N{\rEng}- Right? That's what I would've done. - Glenn!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.41,1:18:24.91,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 来了 - 格伦!\N{\rEng}- Yeah. - Glenn!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.58,1:18:27.58,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 好的 来了 - 我有话跟你说\N{\rEng}- Yes. Thank you. Yes. - I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.13,1:18:32.42,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 怎么了? - 什么?\N{\rEng}- Yes, what? - What? What? What?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.42,1:18:35.80,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这小子比他更懂这个角色\N{\rEng}This kid understands the character better than he does.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.80,1:18:37.09,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你说什么?\N{\rEng}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.09,1:18:38.68,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 把你刚才跟我说的话告诉他 - 不 我不想说\N{\rEng}- Tell him what you just told me. - No, I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.68,1:18:39.76,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,说吧 告诉他\N{\rEng}No, tell him.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.76,1:18:42.22,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我只是觉得你刚才看起来没入戏 仅此而已\N{\rEng}I was just saying you didn't really seem like you were in the scene is all.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.22,1:18:46.64,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 额 这位是谁? - 他谁也不是 关键就在这儿\N{\rEng}- Uh, who is this? - He's nobody. That's the point.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.64,1:18:51.56,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,而且 以我的经验 只有小孩才会那样拿刀\N{\rEng}Also, you know, in my experience, only children hold a knife like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.57,1:18:53.19,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,要是真打 刀应该这么拿\N{\rEng}If it's a serious fight, you hold your knife like this,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.19,1:18:55.15,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 刀刃要垂直于手腕 - 这又不是街头斗殴\N{\rEng}- with the blade square to your wrist. - This is not a street fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.15,1:18:56.74,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,好吧 如果你不追求真实感的话\N{\rEng}Okay, well, if you're not going for realistic,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.74,1:18:58.03,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,那你还得再加点花样\N{\rEng}you might as well add a little flair.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.58,1:19:02.74,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,就像这样\N{\rEng}Like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.74,1:19:04.08,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 别闹了 - 对吧 凯?\N{\rEng}- Cut it out. - Right, Kay?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.08,1:19:07.08,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,行了 行了 谢了您的教程 非常感谢\N{\rEng}Okay. Yeah, okay. Thanks for the tutorial. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.08,1:19:10.83,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,真是太感谢了 今天就到这吧 谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you very much indeed. That's all we need today. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.83,1:19:12.59,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 祝你好运 凯 万事顺利 - 让他滚出去!\N{\rEng}- Best of luck, Kay. Best of luck. - Get him out!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.59,1:19:15.63,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这里不需要你了 非常感谢\N{\rEng}We no longer require your presence. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.63,1:19:18.01,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,恕我直言...\N{\rEng}Well, with all due respect...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.01,1:19:20.09,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,可每套布景都要花掉五千多块\N{\rEng}And yet every set cost more than $5,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.09,1:19:23.35,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我没法打个响指 就把你老婆和钱都搞顺当\N{\rEng}I can't just snap my fingers and get your money and your wife into alignment.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.35,1:19:24.97,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我付你钱是让你想办法的\N{\rEng}I pay you to say no.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.97,1:19:26.68,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,她似乎觉得这是在拿空头支票开玩笑\N{\rEng}She seems to think that this is carte blanche.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.68,1:19:28.77,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我没法在这里完成不可能的任务\N{\rEng}I can't just perform the impossible here.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.77,1:19:32.15,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,如果你管不住她 我就找个能管住的人来\N{\rEng}If you can't control her, I will find someone else who can.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.15,1:19:33.36,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,混蛋\N{\rEng}Asshole.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.07,1:19:41.07,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,洛克威尔先生 洛克威尔先生\N{\rEng}Mr. Rockwell. Mr. Rockwell.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.07,1:19:43.70,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 干什么? - 嘿 马蒂·毛瑟 见到你真好\N{\rEng}- What? - Hey. Marty Mauser. Nice to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.70,1:19:46.50,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,是你往我办公室打电话 说是跟我儿子是哥们的?\N{\rEng}Did you call my office and say you're friends with my son?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.58,1:19:48.96,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 是的 但是... - 该死!\N{\rEng}- Yes. But... - Goddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.96,1:19:51.04,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我没别的办法联系你了 拜托\N{\rEng}I had no other way to get in touch with you. Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.04,1:19:52.67,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我想重新谈谈去日本的事\N{\rEng}I wanna revisit our conversation about Japan.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.67,1:19:54.92,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我重新考虑过了 我想去 我觉得那是绝佳的主意\N{\rEng}I reconsidered it and I wanna do it. I think it's a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.92,1:19:56.84,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,比赛就在下周 我已经有别的打算了\N{\rEng}The event's next week. I've made alternate plans.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.84,1:19:58.55,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,什么打算? 嘿 那可是你的主意\N{\rEng}What other plans? Okay, it was your idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.55,1:20:01.59,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这主意棒极了 咱们就花两秒钟谈谈这事吧\N{\rEng}It's a fantastic idea. Let's just have a conversation about this for two seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.59,1:20:04.18,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你干什么呢? 嘿 嘿 洛克威尔先生\N{\rEng}What are you doing? Hey. Hey. Mr. Rockwell.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.18,1:20:06.10,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,拜托 咱们都现实一点好吗\N{\rEng}Please, let's both be pragmatists about this.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.10,1:20:08.27,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,把你对我的个人成见先放一边\N{\rEng}Put your personal feelings about me aside for a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.27,1:20:11.35,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你我都很清楚 我和远藤古都打能创造多大价值\N{\rEng}You and I both know how much value I would add with Endo.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.35,1:20:13.23,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,在他的主场打表演赛?\N{\rEng}In an exhibition on his home turf?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.23,1:20:15.15,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,想象一下 我就像根炸药引信\N{\rEng}Imagine it. I'd be like a stick of dynamite.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.15,1:20:16.73,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不管你现在的备选方案是什么\N{\rEng}Whatever you have planned, the alternative,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.73,1:20:18.11,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,跟这个比起来都黯然失色\N{\rEng}it's gonna pale in comparison.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.11,1:20:19.32,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,请给我两分钟时间\N{\rEng}Please give me two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.32,1:20:22.49,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,咱们有很多共识能解决这问题 拜托!\N{\rEng}We have enough common ground to figure this out. Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.49,1:20:24.95,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 行吧 上车说 - 真的? 谢谢\N{\rEng}- All right, get in the car. - Really? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.95,1:20:26.16,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,汤米 开车\N{\rEng}Tommy, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.95,1:20:29.25,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 嘿! 嘿! - 嘿!\N{\rEng}- Hey. Hey! Hey! - Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.33,1:20:32.62,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你个狗娘养的 那个主意还是我给你的!\N{\rEng}You son of a bitch. I gave you the idea!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.18,1:20:45.89,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不好意思 斯通小姐让我转告你\N{\rEng}I'm sorry. Miss Stone wanted to let you know
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.89,1:20:47.72,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,她很乐意和你共进午餐\N{\rEng}that she'd love to have lunch with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.72,1:20:49.31,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 斯通小姐? - 是的\N{\rEng}- Miss Stone? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.07,1:21:07.58,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,天哪 我迟到太久了\N{\rEng}My God, I'm so late.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.58,1:21:09.16,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,拜托 你管那么多干嘛?\N{\rEng}Come on. What do you care?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.16,1:21:11.70,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,你可是主角 这感觉应该很爽吧?\N{\rEng}You're the star. Gotta feel pretty good, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.71,1:21:13.58,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,我是说 你当初为什么要息影?\N{\rEng}I mean, why'd you even stop in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.58,1:21:16.17,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我想要稳定 后来我怀孕了\N{\rEng}I wanted security, and I got pregnant,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.09,1:21:19.88,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,加上他的压力 我就妥协了\N{\rEng}and he pressured me, and I settled.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.88,1:21:22.30,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嗯 显然你现在做的是正确决定\N{\rEng}Well, I mean, clearly, you're doing the right thing now
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.30,1:21:24.47,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,而且听起来他正加倍补偿你呢\N{\rEng}and it sounds like he's paying you back with interest.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.47,1:21:26.64,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 谁? - 你丈夫\N{\rEng}- Who is? - Your husband.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.64,1:21:28.22,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我是说 你的整场演出都是他出钱吧?\N{\rEng}I mean, he's funding your whole show, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.22,1:21:29.31,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你哪来的这种想法?\N{\rEng}Where'd you get that idea?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.31,1:21:30.97,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我在大堂无意中听到他在抱怨\N{\rEng}I overheard him complaining about it in the lobby.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.97,1:21:32.81,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 抱怨? - 是的 抱怨开销太大\N{\rEng}- Complaining? - Yeah, about the costs.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.98,1:21:35.52,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,让他滚一边去吧\N{\rEng}He can go fuck himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.52,1:21:37.15,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,没错 彻底滚蛋 你知道你该怎么做\N{\rEng}Completely. You know what you should do,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.15,1:21:39.07,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你应该榨干他的每一分钱\N{\rEng}you should leech him for every penny he's worth,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.07,1:21:40.86,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,坐稳你全球头号巨星的位子\N{\rEng}assume your place as the biggest star on the planet,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.86,1:21:42.74,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,然后狠狠打他那张自大嘴脸\N{\rEng}and then you rub it in his smug little face.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.74,1:21:45.86,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,谢谢 但我真的不需要你来教我做事\N{\rEng}Thank you, but I'm really not looking for life advice from you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.86,1:21:48.87,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不 我只是说你打从一开始就不需要他\N{\rEng}No, I'm just saying you clearly never needed him in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.41,1:21:52.58,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,就像我 我从不接受任何人的帮助\N{\rEng}Like with me, I'm never accepting anyone's help.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.58,1:21:56.71,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我得完全靠自己 纯粹靠我自己的天赋\N{\rEng}I gotta do it completely on my own. Purely on the basis of my own talent.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.71,1:21:59.88,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,否则的话 这种成功就不算数了\N{\rEng}Otherwise it's, like, the success won't even count.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.88,1:22:01.09,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不过这只是我个人的想法\N{\rEng}But that's just me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.09,1:22:03.38,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,是的 这种话听起来倒是容易\N{\rEng}Yes, well, that's very easy to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.38,1:22:06.26,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,说起来容易 做起来可真难\N{\rEng}Well, it's easy to say but it's sure not easy to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.26,1:22:08.47,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我是说 你懂的 所以你才拿钱退出了\N{\rEng}I mean, you know that. That's why you cashed out.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.01,1:22:12.35,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我问你个事\N{\rEng}Let me ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.02,1:22:15.48,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你搞这种乒乓球的小玩意儿能挣钱吗?\N{\rEng}Do you make money at this little table tennis thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.48,1:22:17.73,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 还没呢 - 你有工作吗?\N{\rEng}- Not yet. - Do you have a job?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.31,1:22:20.48,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,没有 我是说 乒乓球就是我的工作\N{\rEng}No. I mean, table tennis is my job.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.48,1:22:21.57,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,那你靠什么生活?\N{\rEng}How do you live?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.57,1:22:22.65,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我靠信念活着\N{\rEng}I live with the confidence
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.65,1:22:24.44,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,只要我相信自己 钱自然会来的\N{\rEng}that if I believe in myself, the money will follow.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.44,1:22:26.99,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,归根结底 我的奋斗不全是为了钱\N{\rEng}Ultimately, my struggle isn't even about money.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.99,1:22:29.16,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你怎么交房租? - 我不交\N{\rEng}- How do you pay rent? - I don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.16,1:22:31.33,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你在回避问题 - 不 我没回避任何事\N{\rEng}- You're avoiding the question. - No, I'm not avoiding anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.33,1:22:33.12,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,那你今天打算怎么解决吃饭问题?\N{\rEng}How do you plan on eating food today?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.12,1:22:36.54,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,说实话 打算等你一走我就叫客房服务\N{\rEng}Honestly, I was gonna order room service the second you leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.54,1:22:39.04,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 漂亮 - 确实 漂亮\N{\rEng}- Nice. - Yeah. Nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.04,1:22:42.21,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,如果你这整套梦想最终没成 你打算怎么办?\N{\rEng}And what do you plan to do if this whole dream of yours doesn't work out?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.21,1:22:44.38,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我压根就没考虑过这种可能\N{\rEng}That doesn't even enter my consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.38,1:22:46.22,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,行吧 也许你应该考虑下\N{\rEng}Okay. Well, maybe it should.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.18,1:22:48.18,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,哇\N{\rEng}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.72,1:22:51.51,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你听起来像我妈 无意冒犯\N{\rEng}You sound like my mom. No offense.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.51,1:22:53.35,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你听起来像个小屁孩\N{\rEng}And you sound like a child.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.35,1:22:55.60,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,噢 是吗? 显然我年纪够大了\N{\rEng}Oh, yeah? Clearly I'm old enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.60,1:22:56.98,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你什么意思?\N{\rEng}And what is that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.98,1:22:58.64,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,意思就是我年纪够大 可以在你复出的节骨眼\N{\rEng}That I'm old enough to fuck you in your hotel room
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.65,1:23:00.52,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,在你酒店房间里把你办了\N{\rEng}in the middle of your big comeback.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.52,1:23:01.65,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你真恶心\N{\rEng}You're disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.03,1:23:05.03,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,祝演出顺利\N{\rEng}Break a leg.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.78,1:23:14.58,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不 我知道 但我当时出城了\N{\rEng}No, I know, but I was out of town
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.58,1:23:16.91,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,所以我昨天才刚收到那份东西\N{\rEng}so I only just received it yesterday for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.46,1:23:20.29,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,听着 不去日本是不可能的\N{\rEng}Well, look, not coming to Japan is not an option.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.92,1:23:24.13,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,好吧 请转告赛斯先生 全额的银行本票\N{\rEng}Okay, well, just let Mr. Sethi know that a cashier's check in the full amount
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.13,1:23:25.71,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,已经在路上了 已经寄出了\N{\rEng}is already on the way to him. It's in the mail.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.59,1:23:27.72,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不 没关系的 但只是...\N{\rEng}No, that's fine, but just...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.72,1:23:29.72,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我不希望有人对我到场有误会\N{\rEng}I don't want any confusion about my attendance.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.72,1:23:31.76,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我会准时出席 比赛开始我就在那儿\N{\rEng}I'm gonna be there. I'm gonna be there when the tournament starts.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.76,1:23:35.14,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 拿到了! - 耶! 太棒了!\N{\rEng}- I got it! - Yes! Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.10,1:23:37.10,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你觉得值多少?\N{\rEng}How much do you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.64,1:23:40.27,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 这东西是假的 - 你说什么叫是假的?\N{\rEng}- This is not real. - What do you mean it's not real?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.27,1:23:42.48,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 彻头彻尾的假货 - 这可是从千万富婆脖子上摘下来的\N{\rEng}- Total fake. - It came from the neck of a millionaire.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.48,1:23:43.90,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我亲眼看着从她脖子上摘下的\N{\rEng}I saw it come off her neck.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.90,1:23:47.94,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我不管哪来的 这就是垃圾\N{\rEng}I don't care where it came from. It's total garbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.95,1:23:49.86,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 廉价首饰 - 廉价首饰?\N{\rEng}- Costume jewelry. - Costume jewelry?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.86,1:23:51.32,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,噢 操\N{\rEng}Oh, fuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.32,1:23:53.41,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你想要的话 我可以出两块钱收了\N{\rEng}If you want, I can give you two bucks for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.03,1:23:56.24,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 喂? - 嘿 迪昂 是我\N{\rEng}- Hello.- Hey, Dion. It's me.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.25,1:23:57.33,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,你怎么样?\N{\rEng}How are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.33,1:24:00.29,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿 你跑哪去了? 你答应过要弄到经销商名单的\N{\rEng}Hey, where have you been? You promised me we'd have a list of distributors.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.29,1:24:01.42,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,我爸今晚就落地了\N{\rEng}My dad lands tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.42,1:24:03.17,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,我这就回去 全力配合你\N{\rEng}I'll come back now and give you my undivided attention.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.17,1:24:04.79,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,先让我跟我妹说两句\N{\rEng}Let me just talk to my sister for a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.80,1:24:07.09,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,瑞秋 马蒂来电话了\N{\rEng}Rachel, Marty's on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.63,1:24:10.38,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 嗨 你在哪呢? - 嗨 瑞秋 听着\N{\rEng}- Hi. Where are you?- Hi, Rachel, listen.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.38,1:24:12.72,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,我夹克里有个狗项圈 明白吗?\N{\rEng}There's a dog collar in my jacket, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.72,1:24:14.64,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,我认识个在新泽西丢了狗的家伙\N{\rEng}I know a guy who lost a dog out in New Jersey.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.64,1:24:16.22,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,他会付大笔赏金\N{\rEng}He'll pay a big reward.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.22,1:24:18.98,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,还有 正门口碗里有一串车钥匙\N{\rEng}Also, there's a set of car keys in a bowl by the front door.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.98,1:24:20.14,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 见着了吗? - 见到了\N{\rEng}- You see them?- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.14,1:24:22.94,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,把钥匙拿上 别让迪昂瞧见\N{\rEng}Grab the keys, and make sure Dion doesn't see you do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.94,1:24:24.02,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿 迪昂\N{\rEng}Hey, Dion.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.02,1:24:26.02,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,能去商店帮我买点生姜吗?\N{\rEng}Can you go to the store and grab me some ginger?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.02,1:24:28.36,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,我晨吐反应特别厉害\N{\rEng}I'm having really bad morning sickness.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.44,1:24:30.53,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\rEng}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.41,1:24:32.95,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,抱歉 油站关门了\N{\rEng}Sorry, station's closed.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.95,1:24:35.20,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,没事 我们不是来加油的\N{\rEng}That's okay. We're not looking for service.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.20,1:24:38.12,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你看见这附近有狗出没吗?\N{\rEng}Did you see a dog come around here?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.12,1:24:40.20,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,没 啥也没见着 你瞧见狗了吗?\N{\rEng}Nah, I ain't seen nothing. You seen a dog?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.21,1:24:42.08,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 差不多这么高 - 什么时候丢的?\N{\rEng}- He's this tall. - When did you lose it?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.08,1:24:43.37,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,几天前\N{\rEng}A few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.38,1:24:46.92,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,克兰伯里有个收容所 往那走大概五英里\N{\rEng}There's a pound down in Cranberry. About five miles that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.92,1:24:48.26,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 也许去那试试 - 我打过电话了\N{\rEng}- Maybe try there. - I called there.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.88,1:24:50.46,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 抱歉 帮不上忙 - 好吧\N{\rEng}- Sorry, can't help you. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.47,1:24:52.47,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.40,1:25:04.86,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他们什么也没瞧见\N{\rEng}They didn't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.03,1:25:09.28,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,咱们去那儿试试\N{\rEng}Let's go try that place.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.86,1:25:49.61,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rEng}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.78,1:25:52.28,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,有人吗?\N{\rEng}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.91,1:25:59.33,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你去哪? - 我去后面瞧瞧\N{\rEng}- Where are you going? - Just gonna check out back.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.00,1:26:10.96,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,噢 操 摩西\N{\rEng}Oh, shit. Moses.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.96,1:26:13.38,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,我们非常感谢全国各地的唱片商和艺术家们\N{\rEng}We're grateful to the record manufacturers and artists
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.38,1:26:14.55,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,全国各地的艺术家们\N{\rEng}all over the country.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.72,1:26:24.48,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿 伙计 嘿 嘿 摩西\N{\rEng}Hey, buddy. Hey. Hey, Moses.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.48,1:26:26.94,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,是我 马蒂 嘿 伙计 噢 操\N{\rEng}It's Marty. Hey, buddy. Oh, fuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.15,1:26:30.23,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿 伙计\N{\rEng}Hey, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.86,1:26:31.94,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,摩西 摩西!\N{\rEng}Moses. Moses!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.94,1:26:34.32,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿 伙计 冷静点 咱们带你回家\N{\rEng}Hey, buddy. Calm down. Let's get you home.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.32,1:26:36.20,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你想回家的 对吧? 咱们回家\N{\rEng}You wanna go home, right? Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.20,1:26:38.28,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,好了 嘿 别别别别别\N{\rEng}Okay. Hey. No, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.28,1:26:41.16,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,刚才为您播放的是佩珀敏特·哈里斯\N{\rEng}And that was Peppermint Harris
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.16,1:26:43.87,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,以及他的那首金曲...\N{\rEng}and that great record of his...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.54,1:26:49.13,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,不过现在是时候暂别这档节目了\N{\rEng}But it's time to hang up the old blunderbuss for now.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.13,1:26:51.13,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,记住 如果你想...\N{\rEng}Remember, if you want any...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.93,1:27:00.26,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 嗨 你好? - 有什么事?\N{\rEng}- Hi, how are you? - Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.26,1:27:02.93,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我们正帮附近丢了狗的人找狗\N{\rEng}We were just searching the area for a lost dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.93,1:27:05.64,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- "我们"? - 我和我丈夫\N{\rEng}- "We"? - My husband and I.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.64,1:27:08.48,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我们的狗几天前在加油站附近丢了\N{\rEng}We lost our dog a couple of days ago out near the gas station
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.02,1:27:11.52,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他们叫我们来这边瞧瞧...\N{\rEng}and they told us to come and check over here...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.52,1:27:13.15,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 既然你是最近的一户人家 - 谁?\N{\rEng}- seeing that you're the closest house. - Who?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.15,1:27:14.28,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,谁? 哪个加油站?\N{\rEng}Who? Which gas station?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.28,1:27:15.44,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我不知道 - 嘿!\N{\rEng}- I don't know. - Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.44,1:27:16.61,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,是那里一个工作的伙计说的\N{\rEng}It was one of the guys that work there.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.61,1:27:18.49,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 噢 伙计 看到你回来真激动 - 他就在那儿!\N{\rEng}- Oh, man, I'm so excited you're back. - There he is!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.49,1:27:20.28,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我觉得你可能找到了我们的狗 - 你们在私闯民宅\N{\rEng}- I think you might've found our dog. - You're trespassing.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.28,1:27:23.12,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不 抱歉 我们没那意思 我们听到后院有狗叫\N{\rEng}No. I'm sorry, that's not our intention. We heard barking in the back.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.12,1:27:24.79,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我压根不知道你在说什么\N{\rEng}I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.79,1:27:26.62,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我的狗 你找到了\N{\rEng}My dog. You found it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.62,1:27:28.21,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我没找着什么狗\N{\rEng}I didn't find any dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.21,1:27:30.37,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你确定?\N{\rEng}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.38,1:27:32.00,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,废话 我确定 你确定?\N{\rEng}Yeah, I'm sure. Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.00,1:27:34.51,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,是啊...\N{\rEng}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.51,1:27:36.59,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我看了你的窗户\N{\rEng}I looked through your window.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.59,1:27:38.22,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我看到我的狗了 - 你居然窥探我的窗户?\N{\rEng}- I saw my dog. - You were looking through my window?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.22,1:27:39.38,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,幸亏我看了 不是吗?\N{\rEng}It was a good thing I did, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.38,1:27:42.30,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,在我叫警察之前 赶紧从我的地盘滚出去\N{\rEng}Get the hell off my property before I call the police.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.30,1:27:43.72,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,该叫警察的是我\N{\rEng}I should call the police.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.72,1:27:45.97,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,行啊 你想近距离看看他吗?\N{\rEng}Okay. You wanna get a closer look at him?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.97,1:27:47.35,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你想近距离看看? - 是的 求你了\N{\rEng}- You wanna closer look? - Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.35,1:27:49.77,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 行 挺好 - 我就让你看个够\N{\rEng}- Okay, good, good. - I'll give you a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.07,1:27:59.36,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿!\N{\rEng}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.82,1:28:00.82,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,冷静点\N{\rEng}Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.45,1:28:02.45,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我很冷静\N{\rEng}I am calm.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.37,1:28:05.45,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 要是再让我看到你这张犹太脸... - 你认真的?\N{\rEng}- If I see your kike face... - Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.45,1:28:08.20,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- ...再敢窥探我的窗户 - 马蒂 快上车!\N{\rEng}- ...looking through my window again... - Marty, get in the car!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.21,1:28:09.46,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗?\N{\rEng}Are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.46,1:28:10.71,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,...我就开枪把它崩了\N{\rEng}...I'm gonna shoot it off.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.71,1:28:13.29,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,没必要那样 我们这就走 马蒂 快上车!\N{\rEng}There's no need for that. We're leaving. Marty, get in!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.29,1:28:14.67,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你在干什么?\N{\rEng}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.26,1:29:47.93,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 钱太多了 太多了 - 不 直接说 他他妈有的是钱\N{\rEng}- It's too much money. It's too much. - No, say it. He's fucking loaded.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.93,1:29:48.93,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 喂? - 告诉他\N{\rEng}- Hello?- Tell him.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.60,1:29:52.81,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我在想 拿两千块钱还算公道\N{\rEng}I was thinking maybe $2,000 seems fair for this kind of a thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.81,1:29:54.31,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我觉得挺公道的\N{\rEng}That seems pretty fair to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.31,1:29:56.06,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 两千 - 你开玩笑呢吧?\N{\rEng}- Two thousand. - You're joking, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.69,1:29:59.32,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 没开玩笑 - 简直他妈的离谱\N{\rEng}- No, no. No. - That's fucking ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.32,1:30:00.32,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,听着 听着...\N{\rEng}Look, look...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.65,1:30:03.78,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我知道这事跟你没关系\N{\rEng}I know it's really not your problem,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.61,1:30:08.41,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,但我快生了 而且 瞧 我现在也没丈夫\N{\rEng}but I'm about to have a baby, and, look, I got no husband right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.41,1:30:11.45,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我没工作 这笔钱真的 真的能帮到我\N{\rEng}I got no job, and this money would really, really help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.45,1:30:13.41,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,而且 你懂的 咱们都是好人...\N{\rEng}And, you know, let's be good people and...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.41,1:30:16.67,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,你知道那条狗是我从收容所免费领的 对吧?\N{\rEng}You realize I got that dog for free at the pound, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.42,1:30:20.17,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,额 那你这看法可就不对了\N{\rEng}Well, that's kind of the wrong way to look at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.17,1:30:22.42,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 噢 是吗? - 是的 真的\N{\rEng}- Oh, really?- Yeah, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.42,1:30:23.92,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,那我该怎么看?\N{\rEng}How am I supposed to look at it?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.92,1:30:26.72,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,咱们就这么说吧 我现在打这电话不是为了狗\N{\rEng}'Cause let's just say that I'm not calling about a dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.72,1:30:28.39,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,假设我这电话是为你妈打的\N{\rEng}Let's say that I'm calling about your mother,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.39,1:30:31.39,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我是个医生 我得给她做急诊手术\N{\rEng}and I'm a doctor, and I gotta perform emergency surgery on her
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.39,1:30:33.06,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,否则她就没命了 你会怎么做?\N{\rEng}or she's gonna die. What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.06,1:30:35.60,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,就因为你妈也是"免费"来的 你就拒绝手术?\N{\rEng}Refuse the surgery because you got your mother for free?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.60,1:30:37.44,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不! 那太疯了 你肯定会同意手术\N{\rEng}No! That's crazy. You're gonna take the surgery
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.44,1:30:39.44,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 因为你爱你妈 - 这是我听过最蠢的话\N{\rEng}- because you love your mother. - That's the stupidest thing I ever heard.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.44,1:30:42.32,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,那我看你压根不懂什么是爱\N{\rEng}Well, then I guess you don't know anything about love.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.32,1:30:45.86,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,行了 别扯了 给我地址 好吗? 我现在就过去\N{\rEng}All right, forget it. Give me your address, okay? I'll come now.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.86,1:30:48.11,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我带现金过去 - 抱歉 但不行\N{\rEng}- I'll bring you the cash.- I'm sorry, but no.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.12,1:30:49.49,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 不行? - 不行\N{\rEng}- No?- No.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.49,1:30:52.83,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这真的不是你的错 听起来你也是个大好人\N{\rEng}it's really not your fault, and you sound like a very nice person.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.83,1:30:55.37,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,只是我以前被坑过太多次了\N{\rEng}It's just I've been ripped off one too many times in the past,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.37,1:30:57.25,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我再也不想让那种事发生了\N{\rEng}and I'm just not willing to let that happen to me again.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.25,1:31:00.42,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,所以 咱们得想个办法 让我先拿到钱\N{\rEng}So, we're just gonna need to find a way to get me the money first.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.42,1:31:01.92,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你懂吗? 对 - 真的吗?\N{\rEng}- You know? Yeah. - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.92,1:31:03.75,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,给我听好了 你这个他妈的臭娘们\N{\rEng}Listen to me, you fucking dumb bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.76,1:31:05.88,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你一分钱也别想拿到... - 你有什么毛病?\N{\rEng}- You're not getting one red cent...- What is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.88,1:31:07.13,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,...除非我亲眼见到它\N{\rEng}...without me laying eyes on him.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.13,1:31:09.72,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 如果你真的不在乎... - 听明白了吗 妹子?\N{\rEng}- If you really don't give a shit about... - You understand, sister?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.72,1:31:12.39,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,...你那只白捡的狗 没准我该把它捐给医学界做研究?\N{\rEng}...your dog that you got for free, how about I donate him to medical science?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.39,1:31:15.22,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你想要那种结果吗? - 我就说这行不通\N{\rEng}- Would that be something you want? - I told you this wasn't gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.23,1:31:16.98,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我早该知道的 我在干什么啊?\N{\rEng}I should have known better. What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.98,1:31:18.23,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 真是个烂主意 - 马蒂!\N{\rEng}- It was a terrible idea. - Marty!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.23,1:31:19.65,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 蠢透了 - 抱歉 我当时想...\N{\rEng}- It was moronic. - I'm sorry, I was--
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.65,1:31:21.90,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我只是想试一把\N{\rEng}I'm sorry. I was trying to give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.90,1:31:24.28,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 不是你的错 是这事太蠢了 - 好了 冷静点\N{\rEng}- It's not your fault. It was stupid. - All right. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.57,1:31:28.53,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,那狗是什么颜色的?\N{\rEng}What color is the dog?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.53,1:31:30.87,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,干嘛? 谁在乎啊 是棕色的\N{\rEng}Why? Who cares? It's brown.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.87,1:31:33.78,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,好吧 因为我老板认识当地所有的育犬师\N{\rEng}Okay, because my boss knows all of the local breeders,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.79,1:31:35.91,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,没准咱们能找只长得一样的\N{\rEng}and maybe we can get one that looks the same,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.91,1:31:37.58,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,主人肯定分不出区别\N{\rEng}and the owner won't be able to tell the difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.58,1:31:39.50,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你觉得他会认不出他心爱的狗?\N{\rEng}You don't think he's gonna recognize his own dog that he loves?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.50,1:31:41.75,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我是说起码一开始认不出 - 我现在本该在练球\N{\rEng}- I'm saying maybe not at first. - I should be working on my game right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.75,1:31:43.42,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,结果我现在却在二手车场\N{\rEng}Instead, I'm in a used car lot
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.42,1:31:46.26,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,玩这种恶作剧电话 把生活搞得像个笑话\N{\rEng}making a mockery of my life, doing prank calls.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.81,1:32:02.77,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你们在干什么? - 嘿 你怎么还没睡?\N{\rEng}- What are you guys doing? - Hey. What are you still doing up?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.77,1:32:04.77,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,小点声 我爸妈在睡觉\N{\rEng}Keep your voice down. My parents are sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.78,1:32:06.53,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我不知道他们回来了 - 我告诉过你他们回来了\N{\rEng}- I didn't know they were back. - I told you they were back.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.53,1:32:08.86,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我爸的车呢? - 在车库里\N{\rEng}- Where's my dad's car? - It's in the garage.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.86,1:32:10.95,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,迪昂 我跟你说 我们这一天过得简直难以置信\N{\rEng}You're not gonna believe, Dion, when I tell you the day that we had.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.95,1:32:13.12,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你骗了我 - 不 我没有 你在说什么呢?\N{\rEng}- You tricked me. - No, I didn't. What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.12,1:32:15.03,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你确实骗了 你这骗子婊子 - 喔\N{\rEng}- Yes, you did, you lying bitch. - Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.04,1:32:16.99,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘴放干净点 你这死肥猪\N{\rEng}Hey, you watch your mouth, you fat piece of shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.00,1:32:18.79,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 别这么跟我说话 - 别这么跟他说话\N{\rEng}- Don't talk to me like that. - Don't talk to him like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.79,1:32:20.00,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他可是我全世界最铁的朋友\N{\rEng}He's one of my favorite people on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.00,1:32:21.71,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 叫他别这么跟我说话 - 别这么跟她说话\N{\rEng}- Tell him not to talk to me like that. - Don't talk to her like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.71,1:32:24.04,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 别这么跟他说话 - 小声点\N{\rEng}- Don't talk to him like that. - Keep it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.04,1:32:26.34,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,是我让她干的 我不开口她肯定不会干\N{\rEng}I'm the one that told her to do it. She wouldn't have if I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.34,1:32:29.17,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 把车钥匙给我 - 行 就在这儿 拿着\N{\rEng}- Give me the car keys. - Okay, they're right here. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.05,1:32:31.63,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 咱们出了点小剐蹭... - 什么?\N{\rEng}- We got into a little fender bender... - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.64,1:32:32.72,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,...但没大碍\N{\rEng}...but it's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.72,1:32:35.39,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 只是点小伤 我会赔的 - 拿什么赔? 什么时候赔?\N{\rEng}- It's minor damage. I can pay for it. - How? When?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.39,1:32:38.52,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,迪昂 这么晚了 咱们都该歇歇了\N{\rEng}Dion, it's very late right now. We should all get a little bit of rest.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.52,1:32:40.02,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,明早吃早饭时我会跟你爸解释清楚\N{\rEng}I'll smooth it over with your father at breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.02,1:32:41.73,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 他不会生气的... - 你们不能住这儿!\N{\rEng}- He's not gonna get angry-- - You're not staying here!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.73,1:32:44.02,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 咱们没别的地方住了 - 你们必须得走\N{\rEng}- We got no other place to stay. - You guys gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.02,1:32:45.44,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不 迪昂 咱们必须得留下\N{\rEng}No. Dion. We have to stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.44,1:32:47.36,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 咱们没处去... 迪昂 别赶人 - 不行 嘘\N{\rEng}- We have nowhere-- Dion. Stop it. - No. Shh.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.36,1:32:49.11,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,她都怀孕八个月了 你疯了吗?\N{\rEng}She's eight months pregnant. Are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.11,1:32:50.82,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 咱们能不能再谈谈? - 声音小点\N{\rEng}- Please can we just talk about it? - Keep your voice down.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.82,1:32:52.15,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,深更半夜的 你要把咱们赶到大街上?\N{\rEng}Gonna throw us out in the street in the dead of night?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.16,1:32:54.78,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 没错 走吧 - 咱们真的没地方去\N{\rEng}- Yeah, yeah. - We've got nowhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.87,1:32:57.83,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,拿上你们的破烂赶紧滚\N{\rEng}Get your shit and leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.83,1:32:58.91,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你知道咱们今天经历了什么吗?\N{\rEng}Do you have any idea what we've been through today?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.91,1:33:00.41,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我没在跟你说话\N{\rEng}I'm not talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.41,1:33:02.25,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你不想跟我说话?\N{\rEng}You're not talking to me?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.25,1:33:04.13,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,现在你彻底不打算跟我说话了?\N{\rEng}Now you're not talking to me, period?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.13,1:33:05.63,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,真离谱\N{\rEng}Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.63,1:33:07.55,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,含着金汤匙出生肯定很爽吧\N{\rEng}Must be nice being born with a silver spoon in your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.55,1:33:09.55,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,而咱们有些人得为了生活奔波\N{\rEng}Meanwhile, some of us have to work for a living.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.55,1:33:11.38,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你听过"工作"这词儿吗?\N{\rEng}You ever heard that word, "work"?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.38,1:33:13.18,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,而不是整天躲屋里涂鸦\N{\rEng}Instead of doodling in your room all day?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.26,1:33:15.93,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,居然把朋友往大街上赶...\N{\rEng}Throwing your friends out on the street...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.93,1:33:19.72,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,别一直盯着咱们看行吗? 看墙去\N{\rEng}Can you not stare at us? Can you look at the wall?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.73,1:33:21.02,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,看得我毛骨悚然\N{\rEng}You're creeping me out.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.22,1:33:23.72,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,咱们要去哪? 因为...\N{\rEng}Where are we gonna go? Because...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.98,1:33:26.15,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 对不住 既然这儿就有张床... - 没事的\N{\rEng}- I'm sorry. You have a bed right here... - It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.15,1:33:28.02,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- ...我本来能睡上面的 - 没事的\N{\rEng}- ...and I could be sleeping on it. - It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.03,1:33:31.28,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我肚里还有个娃呢 我肚里还有个娃呢\N{\rEng}And I got a baby in me. I got a baby in me.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.28,1:33:32.36,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,看看你在干嘛?\N{\rEng}See what you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.36,1:33:34.82,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,大半夜的把孕妇赶出门\N{\rEng}You're throwing a pregnant woman out in the dead of the night.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.82,1:33:36.95,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你会一辈子受良心谴责的\N{\rEng}It's gonna live on your conscience forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.95,1:33:38.91,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你干嘛要这么折磨自己? - 对不起\N{\rEng}- Why would you do this to yourself? - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.91,1:33:40.54,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,能让我陪她待一会儿吗? 我得安慰她\N{\rEng}Can I have a moment with her, please? Just to comfort her,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.54,1:33:42.12,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,跟我亲妹妹单独待会 好吗?\N{\rEng}in privacy with my sister, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.12,1:33:44.50,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 让她小声点 - 我尽量 但我得先让她冷静下来\N{\rEng}- Keep her voice down. - I'm gonna try, but I gotta calm her down.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.50,1:33:46.75,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\rEng}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.25,1:33:49.76,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我不知道该怎么办 我不知道该怎么办\N{\rEng}I don't know what to do. I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.51,1:33:52.92,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,演得真好\N{\rEng}That was really good.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.93,1:33:54.55,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 瑞秋 演得太牛了 - 谢谢\N{\rEng}- That was amazing, Rachel. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.55,1:33:55.76,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,太到位了 没准能成\N{\rEng}That was so good, it might work.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.76,1:33:57.97,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 如果他把咱们赶走 咱们去哪? - 他现在可能真会留咱们住下\N{\rEng}- Where are we gonna go if he kicks us out? - He might actually let us stay now.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.97,1:33:59.76,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,那演技简直绝了\N{\rEng}That acting was so brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.77,1:34:02.52,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你真的在哭吗? - 没 马蒂 你在干什么?\N{\rEng}- Are you actually crying? - No. Marty, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.35,1:34:05.35,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 那是什么? - 什么?\N{\rEng}- What is that? - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.65,1:34:07.81,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这是化妆品?\N{\rEng}Is this makeup?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.32,1:34:12.53,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\rEng}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.53,1:34:15.86,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,等等听我说 听我解释 这不怪我 好吗?\N{\rEng}Just wait. Because I can explain. It's not my fault. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.86,1:34:16.95,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,闭嘴\N{\rEng}No talking.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.95,1:34:19.66,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我也是没法子 你懂吗? - 够了 求你别说了 闭嘴\N{\rEng}- I didn't have a choice, you know? - Stop. Stop, please. Stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.66,1:34:21.33,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 瑞秋 别说了 - 我得离开那儿\N{\rEng}- Rachel, stop. - I needed to get out.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.33,1:34:24.54,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 看到我现在有多冷静了吗? 但快到头了 - 对\N{\rEng}- See how calm I am? It's not gonna last. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.54,1:34:26.00,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,给我滚出去\N{\rEng}Get the fuck out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.00,1:34:27.67,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 不 我觉得... - 给我滚出去\N{\rEng}- No. What I think-- - Get the fuck out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.67,1:34:30.21,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我觉得咱们都该走 因为... - 闭嘴\N{\rEng}- I think that we should both go because... - Stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.21,1:34:31.84,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这种破事也就我妈能干得出来\N{\rEng}This is the kinda shit my mother would do to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.84,1:34:34.13,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,亏我这么对你 偏偏是你 居然也这么对我?\N{\rEng}How could you of all people do this to me, the way I treat you?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.13,1:34:37.47,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我怎么对你了? - 对 明知道我经历了什么还这么干?\N{\rEng}- How could I do this to you? - Yes, knowing what I'm going through?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.47,1:34:39.85,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 那你对我做的这些呢? - 够了 嘘 你在干嘛...\N{\rEng}- How about what you're doing to me? - Stop. Shh. What are you doing...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.85,1:34:42.85,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,哪怕有一秒钟 你考虑过你正在做什么吗...\N{\rEng}Have you ever for one second thought about what you're doing--
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.85,1:34:44.81,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 住口 - 闭上你的臭嘴吧 你这自恋的畜生\N{\rEng}- Stop. - Shush yourself, you narcissistic prick.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.81,1:34:46.64,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 别碰我! - 够了 你们在干什么?\N{\rEng}- Don't touch me! - Stop. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.65,1:34:49.06,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你要把我爸妈吵醒了 闭嘴 - 去他妈的你父母吧\N{\rEng}- You're gonna wake my parents up. Shut up. - Enough about your fucking parents.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.06,1:34:50.48,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你他妈都三十岁的人了 难道不是吗?\N{\rEng}Aren't you, like, 30 years old?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.48,1:34:53.32,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你意识到我还有四周就生了吗?\N{\rEng}You realize I'm due in four weeks?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.32,1:34:55.11,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我还有四周就生了! - 孩子又不是我的\N{\rEng}- I am due in four weeks! - It's not my baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.11,1:34:57.74,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,而且孩子就是他的 顺便说下 真是他妈的孩子\N{\rEng}And it's his baby, by the way. It's his fucking baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.74,1:34:59.32,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这事儿他也在撒谎\N{\rEng}He's lying about that too.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.32,1:35:02.24,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我家出什么事了? - 爸 我只是带几个朋友过来\N{\rEng}- What's going on in my house? - I was just having some friends over, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.24,1:35:03.33,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,伙计 你还好吗?\N{\rEng}Buddy, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.33,1:35:05.62,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿 明早咱们得第一时间和斯伯丁开会\N{\rEng}Hey, we have a meeting with Spalding first thing in the morning
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.62,1:35:07.58,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 为了"至尊"的样球 - 迪昂 算了吧 别演了\N{\rEng}- for the Supreme samples. - Dion, come on. Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.58,1:35:09.21,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,那根本就不可能成\N{\rEng}That's never gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.21,1:35:11.50,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你拿了我儿子的钱 - 您在说什么呢?\N{\rEng}- You've taken my son's money. - What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.50,1:35:14.09,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我不信 迪 难道你看不出来发生了什么吗?\N{\rEng}I don't believe it. D, don't you see what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.09,1:35:16.47,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 简直离谱 太他妈离谱了... - 你一直都在骗我儿子\N{\rEng}- Unbelievable. Un-fucking... - You're conning my son all along.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.47,1:35:18.26,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我才没有骗你儿子 - 你卷走了他所有的钱\N{\rEng}- I am not conning your son. - You're taking all his money.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.26,1:35:20.89,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我给了他生活的意义 哪怕你只给了他钱\N{\rEng}I give him meaning. All you do is give him money.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.89,1:35:22.60,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我给了他奋斗的目标 - 给我听好!\N{\rEng}- I give him purpose. - You listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.60,1:35:25.89,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他他妈看都不敢看你一眼 他怕你怕得要死\N{\rEng}He won't even fucking look at you, he's so petrified of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.89,1:35:28.81,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,咱们怎么办 哈? 你们打算让咱们去哪儿?\N{\rEng}What are we gonna do, huh? Where do you expect us to go?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.81,1:35:31.06,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你真想让我睡大街? 我怀孕了\N{\rEng}You really want me to sleep on the street? I'm pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.06,1:35:32.94,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,别 别 迪昂! 迪昂!\N{\rEng}No, no, no. Dion! Dion!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.38,1:35:59.43,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,行吧 瑞秋 我得告诉你件事 我没想针对你\N{\rEng}All right, I gotta tell you something, Rachel. It's not intended to be mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.43,1:36:02.09,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我有我的使命 而你没有\N{\rEng}I have a purpose. You don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.10,1:36:03.60,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,如果你觉得那算是什么恩赐 那你就大错特错了\N{\rEng}If you think that's some sort of blessing, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.60,1:36:05.85,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,那反倒成了我人生中巨大的劣势\N{\rEng}It puts me at a huge life disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.85,1:36:09.35,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,它意味着我背负着要成就某件事的义务\N{\rEng}It means I have an obligation to see a very specific thing through.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.35,1:36:11.56,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,而那份义务必然伴随着牺牲 懂吗?\N{\rEng}And with that obligation comes sacrifice, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.56,1:36:14.52,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我的人生是我所有被迫做出的选择的产物\N{\rEng}My life is the product of all the choices I've had to make.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.53,1:36:15.90,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,而你的人生则是...\N{\rEng}Your life is the product of...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.90,1:36:17.49,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我都不知道你的人生算什么产物\N{\rEng}I don't even know what your life is the product of.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.49,1:36:19.70,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你过一天算一天 你这种人就这样\N{\rEng}You're making it up as you go. That's the kind of person you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.70,1:36:21.91,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我可不是那种人 懂吗?\N{\rEng}That's not the kind of person I am, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.91,1:36:23.82,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你得为你那些操蛋决定负责\N{\rEng}You're responsible for the shitty decisions you've made.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.83,1:36:25.87,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我从没叫你结婚 一次都没有\N{\rEng}I never told you to get married, not once.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.87,1:36:28.58,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你别想把这些赖在我头上 - 我明白\N{\rEng}- You cannot pawn them off onto me. - I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.58,1:36:30.67,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你在宠物店一年挣多少?\N{\rEng}How much do you make a year at the pet store?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.67,1:36:31.75,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,差不多1200块\N{\rEng}About $1200.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.75,1:36:34.79,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,听着 免得你忘了 我得在一周内弄到1500块\N{\rEng}Okay, in case you forgot, I have a week to make $1500,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.80,1:36:35.92,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,还没算机票呢\N{\rEng}not including air fare.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.92,1:36:38.55,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我现在得专注 别让我分心\N{\rEng}I need to focus right now, no distractions.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.47,1:36:41.97,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 真的很抱歉 - 没事\N{\rEng}- I'm really sorry. - No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.97,1:36:43.93,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,显而易见 我现在没法安定下来\N{\rEng}It goes without saying, I'm in no position to settle down right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.93,1:36:47.14,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,断了这个念头吧 我现在不会安定下来的 好吗?\N{\rEng}Get that out of your mind. I will not settle down right now. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.77,1:36:50.18,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,要是你真打算离开艾拉 我不会抛弃你的\N{\rEng}If you're serious about leaving Ira, I will not abandon you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.19,1:36:52.14,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,作为朋友 我会帮你\N{\rEng}As your friend, I will help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.15,1:36:54.69,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,咱们会去查 找个好的待产院\N{\rEng}We'll do the research, we'll find a great maternity home.
