Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.49,1:44:06.08,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你还要继续玩这套? - 我只是在做自己\N{\rEng}- Are you gonna keep on with this? - Just being myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.08,1:44:08.00,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你满嘴谎话 - 我没有 这就是真实的我\N{\rEng}- You're lying through your teeth. - I'm not. It's me being me.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.00,1:44:10.96,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 真可悲 你在做自己? - 我说的是真话\N{\rEng}- This is pathetic. You're being you? - I am telling you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.96,1:44:13.67,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我偷了你的东西然后感到内疚\N{\rEng}I stole from you and then I feel bad about it,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.67,1:44:15.88,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 所以想来补救 - 别白费劲了 我不在乎\N{\rEng}- so I'm trying to make amends. - You're wasting your energy. I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.88,1:44:17.55,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,换了我也会偷我自己的\N{\rEng}I would have stolen from me too.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.34,1:44:20.55,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,凯\N{\rEng}Kay.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.26,1:44:24.81,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 嗨 - 看来我打断你们了\N{\rEng}- Hi. - Looks like I'm interrupting something.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.81,1:44:25.89,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不 不 没那回事\N{\rEng}No, no. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.89,1:44:28.64,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这位是马丁 我朋友卡罗尔的儿子 他正要走\N{\rEng}This is Martin, my friend Carol's son. He was just leaving.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.64,1:44:31.23,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 这位是默尔 我的公关 - 你好\N{\rEng}- This is Merle, my publicist. - Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.23,1:44:35.07,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,马丁想当个演员 但可惜他演技不太行\N{\rEng}Martin would like to be an actor, but unfortunately he's not very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.07,1:44:36.78,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,额 那个\N{\rEng}Ah, well, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.78,1:44:39.53,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 百老汇也需要领位员嘛 - 座位安排得怎么样了?\N{\rEng}- Broadway needs ushers too. - So what's happening with the seating?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.53,1:44:42.70,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我跟米尔顿谈过了 他会派所有员工过来\N{\rEng}I spoke to Milton. He's sending all of his employees.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.70,1:44:44.78,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,就像强制任务 公司的内部指标\N{\rEng}It's like a mandate. Like, a company mandate.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.79,1:44:46.24,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这就能让我高兴了?\N{\rEng}This is supposed to make me happy?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.25,1:44:48.83,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我是说 既然座无虚席 目的不就达到了吗?\N{\rEng}Well, I mean, it's a full house. Isn't that the point?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.83,1:44:51.29,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,满座的他妈的蠢货 - 不 没那么糟 里面还有点--\N{\rEng}Full of fucking morons. - No, no. You got some--
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.29,1:44:53.38,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 弗雷德·阿斯泰尔要来 - 好 我不在这儿碍事了\N{\rEng}- Fred Astaire is coming. - Okay, I'm gonna get out your hair...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.38,1:44:56.17,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,别 一定要给他一张今晚的票\N{\rEng}No. Make sure you give him a ticket for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.17,1:44:58.59,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 真的? - 是啊\N{\rEng}- Really? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.59,1:45:01.97,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,噢 小伙子 你这下有福了\N{\rEng}Oh. You are in for such a treat, young man.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.97,1:45:03.30,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,当你看到这位女士演戏时\N{\rEng}When you see this lady act,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.30,1:45:06.26,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你会觉得就像被吸尘器口爆了一样\N{\rEng}you're gonna feel like you got your cock sucked by a vacuum cleaner.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.27,1:45:08.56,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 默尔! - 她脸红了 看见没?\N{\rEng}- Merle! - She's blushing. See her?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.56,1:45:10.81,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,什么?\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.56,1:45:53.40,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,坐回你那臭位子上\N{\rEng}Take your stinking seat.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.65,1:46:00.65,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼?\N{\rEng}What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.20,1:46:03.70,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你他妈疯了吗?\N{\rEng}Have you lost your damned mind?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.12,1:46:12.66,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,杰德 我在跟你说话\N{\rEng}Jed. I'm talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.25,1:46:15.92,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我只是在练准头 妈\N{\rEng}I was just practicing my aim, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.92,1:46:19.38,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你总说做人要有大志向\N{\rEng}You always said to shoot for the stars.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.68,1:46:27.68,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\rEng}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.43,1:46:29.43,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,过来\N{\rEng}Come.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.06,1:46:33.56,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,抱歉迟到了 脱不开身\N{\rEng}I'm sorry I'm late. I couldn't get away.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.56,1:46:35.60,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 呵 我信 - 他一直缠着我\N{\rEng}- Oh, I bet. - He was all over me.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.60,1:46:37.44,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你今晚棒极了 简直不可思议\N{\rEng}You were incredible tonight. That was unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.44,1:46:39.36,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我有东西送你 - 给我的?\N{\rEng}- I have something for you. - For me?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.90,1:46:40.90,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,转过去\N{\rEng}Turn around.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.32,1:46:47.32,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,每年结婚纪念日我丈夫都会送我一件珠宝\N{\rEng}Every year my husband gives me a piece of jewelry for our anniversary.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.28,1:46:51.33,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我有25件了 每一件都代表一年的痛苦\N{\rEng}I have 25 of them. One for each year of misery.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.20,1:46:54.04,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这够你那趟路费了 没准还有剩\N{\rEng}That should cover your trip and then some.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.17,1:46:57.38,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,戴着这玩意儿让我觉得反胃\N{\rEng}Wearing it makes me feel like shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.64,1:47:11.47,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,噢 操 停下 停下 停下\N{\rEng}Oh, shit. Stop, stop, stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.47,1:47:13.48,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,停\N{\rEng}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.35,1:47:53.35,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿! 嘿 你们在干什么?\N{\rEng}Hey! Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.89,1:47:56.39,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 该死 天哪 - 站起来!\N{\rEng}- Shit. Oh, God. - Get up!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.39,1:47:59.02,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 别乱动 - 站起来 我看见你了\N{\rEng}- Lay still. - Stand up, I see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.02,1:48:02.02,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,听我口令就跑 一 二 三 起\N{\rEng}When I tell you, run. One, two, three. Get up.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.02,1:48:04.03,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 快点 跑 - 嘿!\N{\rEng}- Come on. Go. - Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.03,1:48:05.74,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,乔伊 拦住他们!\N{\rEng}Joey, stop them!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.74,1:48:07.53,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,快点 快点 快点\N{\rEng}Come on. Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.53,1:48:10.66,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿 你们去哪? 跑这儿干嘛呢?\N{\rEng}Hey. Hey. Where are you guys going? What are you guys doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.66,1:48:11.78,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 没干嘛 - 不 不 不\N{\rEng}- Nothing. - No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.78,1:48:13.28,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 让我看到你们的双手 - 铐上他\N{\rEng}- Let me see both of your hands. - Cuff him.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.29,1:48:15.16,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 噢 天哪 我们只是... - 我们什么都没干\N{\rEng}- Oh, my God. We were just... - We didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.16,1:48:18.12,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,饶了我们吧 我们在草地里找她的耳环\N{\rEng}Give us a break. We were looking for her earrings in the grass.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.12,1:48:20.21,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我的耳环掉了 我们在找我的耳环\N{\rEng}My earring came off. We were looking for my earring.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.21,1:48:22.25,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,瞧你耳朵上不是挂着两只吗\N{\rEng}It looks like you've got two earrings in your ears there.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.25,1:48:25.38,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不是这只 是... 之前的 还有一只\N{\rEng}Not this earring. There was... From before. There was another earring.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.38,1:48:28.72,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,今天早些时候还有另一对耳环\N{\rEng}There's another pair of earrings from earlier in the day.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.72,1:48:30.18,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我认得你\N{\rEng}I recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.18,1:48:32.89,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 噢 天哪 - 你是凯·斯通\N{\rEng}- Oh, God. Oh, God. - You're Kay Stone.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.89,1:48:35.22,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 没错 我太清楚你是谁了 - 见鬼了\N{\rEng}- Yes. I know exactly who you are. - This is not happening.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.22,1:48:37.27,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 让我看到你的手 - 你认真的吗?\N{\rEng}- Let see your hands. - Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.27,1:48:39.81,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这样吧 我回家取个钱包\N{\rEng}You know, I will go home,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.81,1:48:42.36,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,拿点现金给你们 毕竟给你们添麻烦了\N{\rEng}and I'll get my wallet, and I will get you some cash because we've put you out.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.90,1:48:46.19,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 拜托 长官 她这就回家拿钱包 给你现金\N{\rEng}- Please, officer. She's gonna go home and get her wallet. And give you cash.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.19,1:48:48.53,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 有证件吗? - 没 没证件\N{\rEng}- Got ID? - No. No ID.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.03,1:48:50.57,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 铐上她 - 别 拜托\N{\rEng}- Cuff her. - No, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.57,1:48:53.20,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 没证件是吧? 让我搜搜 - 拜托了 别这样\N{\rEng}- No ID, huh? Let's see. - Please, please. No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.08,1:48:56.04,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 拜托 让我回家行吗? - 少废话\N{\rEng}- Please, will you just let me go home? - Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.04,1:48:57.50,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我向你保证\N{\rEng}I'll give you my word.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.50,1:49:01.67,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,哇 瞧瞧 真是条漂亮的项链\N{\rEng}Wow, lookie here. That's a really nice necklace.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.67,1:49:04.54,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,拿去 拿去吧 归你了\N{\rEng}Take it. Take it. It's yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.55,1:49:06.34,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,太感谢了\N{\rEng}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.17,1:49:08.72,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信\N{\rEng}I can't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.63,1:49:11.47,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你能再帮我弄条项链吗?\N{\rEng}Do you think you could grab me another necklace?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.47,1:49:12.55,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你认真的吗?\N{\rEng}Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.55,1:49:14.68,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你说这些对你没意义 就几分钟的事\N{\rEng}You said them mean nothing to you. It'd just take you a couple of minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.68,1:49:17.18,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我才刚消失了半小时 不能上去又马上下来\N{\rEng}I was just gone for half an hour. I can't go up and come right back down.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.18,1:49:19.56,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我妈在那呢 - 你刚才给警察倒是挺爽快\N{\rEng}- My mother is up there. - You'd do that for the police officers.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.56,1:49:22.10,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 噢天呐 我的头发 - 我在走廊等\N{\rEng}- Oh, my God. My hair. - I'll wait in the hall.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.10,1:49:23.52,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不 准跟着\N{\rEng}No, you will not.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.69,1:49:26.44,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,等等 等等\N{\rEng}Wait. Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.94,1:49:29.36,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\rEng}There.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.36,1:49:30.36,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你真美\N{\rEng}You look beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.45,1:49:32.82,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,拜托 你有25条呢\N{\rEng}Please, you have 25 of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.82,1:49:34.16,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,行了!\N{\rEng}Fine!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.16,1:49:36.70,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 待这儿 明白吗? - 我在这待着 好吧\N{\rEng}- Stay here. Do you understand me? - I'll stay here. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.70,1:49:38.12,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 别乱动 - 好的\N{\rEng}- Do not move. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:46.17,1:49:47.17,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,妈的\N{\rEng}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:55.22,1:49:57.60,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你好 很高兴见到你们\N{\rEng}Hello. Lovely to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.60,1:50:00.31,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 大卫 你好吗? - 挺好 你呢?\N{\rEng}- David, how are you? - Good. How are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.52,1:50:07.36,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你他妈死哪去了?\N{\rEng}Where the fuck have you been?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.36,1:50:09.69,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我想清静一会儿 有问题吗?\N{\rEng}I needed a moment to myself. Is that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.69,1:50:11.90,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我不知道出门还得请示\N{\rEng}I didn't realize I needed a permission slip.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:11.90,1:50:14.78,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我为你操办了这一切 你却让我像个蠢货\N{\rEng}I put this whole thing on for you and you're making me look like an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:14.78,1:50:15.87,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\rEng}God.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.87,1:50:18.91,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,听着 默尔正跟《纽约时报》通电话\N{\rEng}Look. Merle's on the phone right now with The New York Times.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.91,1:50:19.99,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,什么?\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.00,1:50:21.45,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他找了个排版员正读剧评呢\N{\rEng}He's got a printer who's gonna read the review.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.46,1:50:22.54,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\rEng}My God.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:22.54,1:50:24.62,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 还是说你压根不在乎? - 接通了! 接通了!\N{\rEng}- Or do you not care? - I got him! I have him!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.63,1:50:26.29,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 噢天呐 来了 - 快来 快来!\N{\rEng}- Oh, my God. Okay. - Come, come, come!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.29,1:50:27.63,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,来了!\N{\rEng}Coming!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.63,1:50:29.34,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 快点 拿到剧评了! - 来了\N{\rEng}- Hurry, he has the review! - I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.34,1:50:30.71,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,剧评!\N{\rEng}The review!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.71,1:50:32.22,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,快点 快点 快点\N{\rEng}Come on, come on, come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.22,1:50:34.05,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 快来 - 来了\N{\rEng}- Come on, come on. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.05,1:50:36.05,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,拉乌尔 凯\N{\rEng}Raoul, Kay.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.05,1:50:40.81,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,好了 标题 "凯·斯通回归" 作者罗伯特...\N{\rEng}Okay. Title, "Kay Stone Returns" by Robert...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.40,1:50:54.61,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 祝今晚愉快 - 门开着 大家都要下来了\N{\rEng}- Have a good night. - Leave it open. Everyone's coming down.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.61,1:50:55.78,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 是吗? - 是啊\N{\rEng}- Are they? - Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.49,1:50:57.49,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,派对结束了\N{\rEng}Party's over.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.99,1:50:59.99,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\rEng}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.38,1:51:10.63,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,派对结束了\N{\rEng}The party's over.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.63,1:51:13.17,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 他们在赶咱们走 - 什么意思? 咱们才刚到\N{\rEng}- They're asking us to leave. - What do you mean? We just got here.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.17,1:51:15.43,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他们该在门口拦住咱们的 凭什么让咱们进来?\N{\rEng}They should've stopped us at the door. Why'd they let us in?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.35,1:51:22.10,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,打扰下 你知道凯在哪儿吗?\N{\rEng}Excuse me. Do you know where Kay is?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.10,1:51:24.52,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 她在楼上卧室 - 好的\N{\rEng}- She's upstairs in her bedroom. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.94,1:52:12.86,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嗨 凯在里面吗?\N{\rEng}Hi. Is Kay in there?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.40,1:52:15.61,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,现在不方便\N{\rEng}This is not a good time.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:15.61,1:52:17.40,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,好的 但我能跟她谈谈吗?\N{\rEng}Okay, but can I just speak to her?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:17.40,1:52:20.32,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我说了 现在真的不方便\N{\rEng}As I said, it's really not a good time.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:51.81,1:52:54.69,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,到年底 如果这人帮你挣了钱 你就留着他\N{\rEng}At the end of the year, if the guy made you money, you keep him.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.69,1:52:57.40,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,否则你就让他滚蛋\N{\rEng}And if not, you throw the bum out.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.40,1:52:58.65,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,打扰下\N{\rEng}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.28,1:53:02.16,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 嗨 - 你在开玩笑吧\N{\rEng}- Hi. - You gotta be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.16,1:53:04.78,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 抱歉上门打扰 - 你是怎么进我家的?\N{\rEng}- I'm sorry to disturb you in your home. - How did you get in my house?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:04.79,1:53:07.58,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,请再给我一次机会 我都给你跪下了\N{\rEng}Please give me another chance. I am on my hands and knees.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.58,1:53:11.29,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我得去日本 还需要1500块参加锦标赛\N{\rEng}I need a ride to Japan and I need $1,500 so I can compete in the championship.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.29,1:53:13.75,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我非常 非常需要这份工作\N{\rEng}I need this job very, very badly.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:13.75,1:53:15.29,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我求你了\N{\rEng}I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.30,1:53:18.42,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我随你怎么使唤 故意输球也行\N{\rEng}I'll work for you however you want. I will lose.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.42,1:53:22.09,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,除了让你的活动圆满成功 我没任何个人立场\N{\rEng}I'll have no personal point of view apart from making your event a success.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:22.09,1:53:25.10,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,马蒂 人生没有第二次机会\N{\rEng}Marty, there are no second chances in life.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.10,1:53:27.39,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 凭什么没有? - 我给过你工作 你拒绝了!\N{\rEng}- Why not? - I offered you the job and you said no!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.39,1:53:30.35,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我知道 那是因为我冲动 我后悔了\N{\rEng}I know, because I was impulsive. And I regret it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:30.35,1:53:31.64,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,然后呢?\N{\rEng}And?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.65,1:53:34.27,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,然后就是我太无礼 太自负了\N{\rEng}And I was rude and overconfident.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:34.27,1:53:36.02,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我太狂妄了 态度也有问题\N{\rEng}And I was cocky, and I copped an attitude.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:36.02,1:53:37.11,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,还有呢?\N{\rEng}And?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:37.11,1:53:38.94,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,绝不会有下次了 对不起\N{\rEng}And it won't happen again. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.94,1:53:40.86,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,请再给我一次机会 洛克威尔先生\N{\rEng}Please just give me another chance, Mr. Rockwell.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.11,1:53:44.62,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我任凭你发落 让我做什么都行\N{\rEng}I'm throwing myself at your mercy. I'll do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:44.62,1:53:47.20,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你们怎么看? 我该给这小混蛋第二次机会吗?\N{\rEng}What do you guys think? Should I give this little asshole a second chance?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.20,1:53:48.87,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 拜托 给吧! - 别问我\N{\rEng}- Yes, please! - Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.87,1:53:51.71,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你不知道这对我有多重要 拜托 我求你了\N{\rEng}You don't know how important this is to me. Please. I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:51.71,1:53:54.08,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,就让我搭你的飞机 让我跟你们一起去\N{\rEng}Just let me go on your plane, and let me join you there.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.08,1:53:56.17,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,拜托 我是在低声下气地求你\N{\rEng}Please, I'm humbling myself before you.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:56.17,1:53:58.59,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 看着你就反胃 - 对不起\N{\rEng}- You're making me sick. - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.59,1:54:00.13,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 站起来! - 好的 行\N{\rEng}- Stand up! - Okay. All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.63,1:54:03.59,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,拜托 好吗? 我什么都肯做\N{\rEng}Please. Okay? I'll do anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:03.59,1:54:05.55,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 什么都肯做? - 是的 任何事\N{\rEng}- Anything? - Yes. Anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.10,1:54:07.18,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,行吧\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.18,1:54:10.43,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,顺着走廊走 右手边第二扇门是我办公室\N{\rEng}Go down the hall. Second door on the right is my office.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:10.43,1:54:13.35,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,去把球拍拿来\N{\rEng}Grab the paddle and bring it back here.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:13.35,1:54:15.73,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这比戏里演得还带劲\N{\rEng}This is more dramatic than the play.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:15.73,1:54:17.48,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 好的 - 确实\N{\rEng}- Okay. - That's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.50,1:54:36.46,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,噢 马蒂 把球拍给我\N{\rEng}Oh, Marty. Give me the paddle.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.92,1:54:39.96,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,听好了 我要你这么做\N{\rEng}So here's what I want you to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.96,1:54:43.13,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我要你趴在椅子上 把裤子脱了\N{\rEng}I want you to bend over that chair and drop your pants.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:45.22,1:54:46.59,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你认真的?\N{\rEng}Are you for real?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.60,1:54:49.10,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你真是个淘气坏小子 现在该打屁股了\N{\rEng}You've been a really bad boy. Now you're gonna get a spanking.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:49.10,1:54:50.68,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,别这样 你认真的吗?\N{\rEng}Come on. Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:50.68,1:54:52.14,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你想去日本的 对吧?\N{\rEng}You wanna get to Japan, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:52.14,1:54:54.23,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,是的 我想去日本 但这就是你想要的?\N{\rEng}Yeah, I wanna go to Japan. But this is what you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.23,1:54:56.65,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,必须得这么干 趴好\N{\rEng}That's what it's gonna take. Now bend over.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.48,1:55:01.15,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,好吧 说清楚\N{\rEng}Okay, so to be clear,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.15,1:55:04.49,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你带我去日本 然后再给我报酬?\N{\rEng}you're gonna bring me to Japan and then you're gonna compensate me?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:04.49,1:55:07.07,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,明早八点半 拉瓜迪亚机场 咱们出发去日本\N{\rEng}Tomorrow morning, 8:30, LaGuardia. We're on our way to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:07.07,1:55:09.66,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我需要票吗? - 飞机是我的\N{\rEng}- Do I need a ticket? - I own the plane.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:09.66,1:55:11.24,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我怎么知道你会说话算数?\N{\rEng}How do I know you're gonna honor this?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:11.25,1:55:14.87,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你不知道 因为你没资格讨价还价\N{\rEng}You don't. Because you have no power here.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:14.87,1:55:16.29,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,趴好\N{\rEng}Now bend over.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.56,1:55:32.93,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,手放这儿 弧度要漂亮点\N{\rEng}Put your hands over here. I want a nice arc.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:32.93,1:55:35.56,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,开始吧\N{\rEng}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:36.35,1:55:37.65,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,噢 天呐\N{\rEng}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:38.90,1:55:40.65,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,行了 我准备好了\N{\rEng}Okay, I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:42.48,1:55:44.69,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这一下是替我儿子打的\N{\rEng}This one is for my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:47.99,1:55:49.45,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.45,1:55:51.16,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这一下是为我自己\N{\rEng}This one is for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.79,1:55:54.16,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,该死!\N{\rEng}God!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:54.16,1:55:55.75,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,现在是加分环节\N{\rEng}Now the bonus round.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:58.46,1:56:03.13,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,漂亮的球拍 一面是木头 一面是海绵\N{\rEng}Beautiful paddle. One side's wood and the other is foam.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.35,1:56:18.48,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 马蒂 怎么样? - 嘿 泰德 嘿 劳伦斯\N{\rEng}- Hey, Marty, how you doin'? - Hey, Ted. Hey, Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:18.48,1:56:20.69,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,噢 妈的 嘿 伙计 近来可好?\N{\rEng}Aw, damn. Hey, man. How you doin'?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.69,1:56:22.65,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你看我今晚能住后屋吗?\N{\rEng}You think I could stay in the back room tonight?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:22.65,1:56:25.11,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,哇 伙计 布莱恩今晚住那儿\N{\rEng}Wow, man. I got Brian staying there tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:25.11,1:56:28.07,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我本想让你住家里的 但我老婆不答应\N{\rEng}I would let you stay at the house, man, but the wife ain't havin' it.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:28.07,1:56:30.20,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我就在这儿晃悠到起飞吧\N{\rEng}I'm just gonna hang around until my flight.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:30.20,1:56:31.37,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你要去哪?\N{\rEng}Where you goin'?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:31.37,1:56:32.99,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,去日本 明早八点出发\N{\rEng}Going to Japan. Tomorrow morning, 8:00 a.m.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.99,1:56:34.74,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 噢耶! - 好样的小伙子!\N{\rEng}- Oh, yeah! - My man!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:34.75,1:56:37.25,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 哟 你真要去啦! 弄到钱了 - 是啊 是啊\N{\rEng}- Yo, you goin'! You got that money. - Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:37.25,1:56:39.12,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,真为你高兴 伙计\N{\rEng}Good for you, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:39.12,1:56:40.83,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你看着一点都不兴奋啊\N{\rEng}You ain't even look like you excited.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:40.83,1:56:43.17,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,没 我... 我挺好的 我挺好\N{\rEng}No, I'm-- I'm good. I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:43.17,1:56:46.51,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,知道你那哥们沃利在后头吧 他一直在等你\N{\rEng}You know your boy back there, Wally, he's been waitin' on you.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:46.51,1:56:47.92,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 沃利在这儿? - 沃利 对\N{\rEng}- Wally's here? - Wally, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:47.93,1:56:50.34,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 他怎么样? - 沃利挺好 挺淡定的 伙计\N{\rEng}- How'd he seem? - Wally's good. He cool, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.34,1:56:51.64,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他就在后头哪待着呢\N{\rEng}He's back there somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:51.64,1:56:54.93,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他看好你 他出一块 她出一块\N{\rEng}He believes in you. He has a dollar. She has a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.47,1:56:57.73,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿 怎么样?\N{\rEng}Hey. How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:58.48,1:57:00.98,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,噢 哇! 见到你真高兴! 怎么样?\N{\rEng}Oh, wow! How you doing? Nice to see you!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:00.98,1:57:02.56,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我一直想联系你\N{\rEng}I've been trying to get in touch with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:02.56,1:57:05.11,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 噢 真的? - 是啊 你的狗呢? 摩西怎么样了?\N{\rEng}- Oh, really? - Yeah. How's your dog? How's Moses doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:05.11,1:57:06.28,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你能别废话了吗?\N{\rEng}You wanna cut the bullshit?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:06.28,1:57:08.07,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,没废话 我是真的关心他\N{\rEng}No bullshit. I'm genuinely concerned about him.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:08.07,1:57:09.65,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 马蒂 你没事吧 伙计? - 没事 我挺好\N{\rEng}- Marty. You good, man? - Yeah, I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:09.66,1:57:11.70,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,现在 听我说 听着 听着 听着\N{\rEng}Now, listen to me. Listen. Listen. Listen.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:11.70,1:57:14.70,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你那小妞就在楼下车里 她正等你呢\N{\rEng}I got your girl downstairs in the car. She's waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:14.70,1:57:17.08,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你他妈在说什么? 瑞秋在你那儿?\N{\rEng}What the fuck are you telling me? You got Rachel?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:17.08,1:57:18.16,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,对\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:18.16,1:57:21.62,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,她跟我说我的狗在新泽西某处 而且你有地址\N{\rEng}She told me my dog's in Jersey somewhere. And you got the address.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:21.63,1:57:23.08,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 好的 - 咱们走\N{\rEng}- Okay. - Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.09,1:57:25.63,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,行吧 好吧 让我...\N{\rEng}Okay. All right. Let me, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:25.63,1:57:28.21,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,额 行吧 让我先...\N{\rEng}Um, okay, let me just...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.22,1:57:30.84,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,给我两秒钟 我就跟我哥们说句话\N{\rEng}Give me two seconds. I just wanna say one thing to my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:30.84,1:57:33.09,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,给你两秒钟行 但老子可不等你\N{\rEng}Give you two seconds, yeah, but I'm not gonna be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:33.10,1:57:35.05,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你要去哪? - 我去哪?\N{\rEng}- Where you gonna be? - Where am I gonna be?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:35.06,1:57:38.27,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我这就下楼拿榔头砸你那小妞的肚子\N{\rEng}I'm gonna be downstairs taking a hammer to your girl's stomach.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:38.27,1:57:39.39,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这就是我要干的事\N{\rEng}That's where I'm gonna be.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:40.98,1:57:43.44,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,行了 知道了 知道了\N{\rEng}Okay. All right. All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:43.44,1:57:44.82,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,喂 毛瑟!\N{\rEng}Yo, Mouse!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:46.61,1:57:48.69,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 搞快点 走 - 好吧\N{\rEng}- Come on. Let's go. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:50.78,1:57:53.91,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,父母留给咱们的钱 他的那份大半都被我拿了\N{\rEng}Well, I took most of his share of the money that our parents left us.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:53.91,1:57:56.41,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你花了你弟的钱? - 是的\N{\rEng}- You spent your brother's money? - Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:56.41,1:57:57.74,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,呵 看来你挺疼你弟的?\N{\rEng}Yeah, you love your brother?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:57.74,1:58:01.04,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,也许你能给我弟安排个差事 你知道他是个讲究人\N{\rEng}Maybe you could give my brother a job. You know he's a good man.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:01.04,1:58:03.25,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我把你的差事给他 行了吧? 米奇 帮个忙\N{\rEng}I'll give him your job, okay? Mitch, do me a favor.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:03.25,1:58:04.25,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,干嘛?\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:04.75,1:58:07.00,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,闭嘴 行吗?\N{\rEng}Stop talking. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:12.13,1:58:14.18,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,好了 看到那边的加油站了吗?\N{\rEng}Okay. See the gas station there?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:15.10,1:58:16.30,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,左手边那栋房子就是\N{\rEng}it's the house to the left.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:16.31,1:58:17.39,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 下个左转口? - 对\N{\rEng}- Next left? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:17.39,1:58:18.39,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,知道了\N{\rEng}I got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:37.66,1:58:40.08,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,下车 赶紧的\N{\rEng}Get out of the car. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:40.62,1:58:41.71,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,米奇 过来\N{\rEng}Mitch, come.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:42.41,1:58:45.42,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 鲁本 你看着她 - 噢 好的\N{\rEng}- Reuben, you wait with her. - Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:47.42,1:58:48.46,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,老实坐着\N{\rEng}Sit tight.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:05.69,1:59:06.69,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,搞快点 使劲敲\N{\rEng}Come on. Louder.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:07.61,1:59:08.90,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,敲响点\N{\rEng}Knock louder.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:14.53,1:59:15.82,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,那是我的狗\N{\rEng}That's my dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:16.70,1:59:19.08,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,摩西! 喂!\N{\rEng}Moses! Yo!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:19.08,1:59:20.20,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,开门!\N{\rEng}Open up!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:21.20,1:59:23.87,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,操 摩西\N{\rEng}Fuck. Moses.
