Dialogue: 0,1:59:27.67,1:59:29.67,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,摩西!\N{\rEng}Moses!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:31.55,1:59:32.76,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,摩西!\N{\rEng}Moses!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:33.38,1:59:35.18,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,那是我的狗 摩西!\N{\rEng}That's my dog. Moses!
