Dialogue: 0,1:59:37.68,1:59:39.10,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,瞧见里头有什么没?\N{\rEng}See anything in there?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:39.10,1:59:40.43,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,没 啥也没瞧见\N{\rEng}No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:46.56,1:59:48.23,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 马蒂! - 妈的\N{\rEng}- Marty! - Shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:49.44,1:59:50.94,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,马蒂! 快跑!\N{\rEng}Marty! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:53.99,1:59:55.36,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,马蒂!\N{\rEng}Marty!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:01.03,2:00:02.33,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,趴下! 趴下!\N{\rEng}Get down! Get down!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:09.00,2:00:10.00,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,操!\N{\rEng}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:16.97,2:00:19.59,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,马蒂! 马蒂! 我中弹了!\N{\rEng}Marty! Marty! I got shot!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:19.60,2:00:20.60,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,救命!\N{\rEng}Help!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:21.35,2:00:23.39,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,救命 马蒂! 求你帮帮我!\N{\rEng}Help, Marty! Please help!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:23.39,2:00:24.39,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,救命!\N{\rEng}Help!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:26.10,2:00:28.77,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你没事吧? 噢不! 你还好吗?\N{\rEng}Are you okay? Oh, no! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:28.77,2:00:30.15,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你还好吗? - 这他妈是怎么回事?\N{\rEng}- Are you okay? - What the fuck's going on?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:30.15,2:00:31.61,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,好了 没事的\N{\rEng}Okay. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:31.61,2:00:33.52,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我流血了 我在流血\N{\rEng}I'm bleeding, I'm bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:33.53,2:00:35.40,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,好了 没事了 没事了 没事了\N{\rEng}Okay. It's okay. It's okay. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:40.95,2:00:42.66,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 真的很抱歉 - 对不起\N{\rEng}- I'm so sorry. - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:42.66,2:00:43.99,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 快去拿钱 - 什么钱?\N{\rEng}- Go get the money. - What money?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:43.99,2:00:47.04,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,快去拿钱 就在他口袋里 在他兜里\N{\rEng}Go get the money. It's in his pocket. It's in his pocket.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:47.04,2:00:48.12,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你确定?\N{\rEng}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:48.12,2:00:50.79,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 钱! 就在内兜里! - 好的 知道了 知道了\N{\rEng}- The money! It's in the inside pocket! - Okay, okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:03.18,2:01:05.10,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,噢 操\N{\rEng}Oh, fuck.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:11.86,2:01:14.86,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这什么玩意?\N{\rEng}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:16.53,2:01:17.82,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,噢 你这混蛋...\N{\rEng}Oh, you motherfucker...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:33.79,2:01:36.92,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,好了 好了 没事了 没事了\N{\rEng}Okay. Okay. Okay. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:39.80,2:01:42.05,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,怎么回事? 操!\N{\rEng}What happened? Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:44.72,2:01:47.56,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,撒开我! 你想上哪儿去?\N{\rEng}Get off me! Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:47.56,2:01:48.73,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\rEng}it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:50.52,2:01:51.60,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,行了\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:53.36,2:01:55.57,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 拿到了吗? 拿到了吗? - 嗯 拿到了 拿到了\N{\rEng}- You got it? You got it? - Yeah. I got it, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:55.57,2:01:56.94,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,钱到手了吗?\N{\rEng}You got the money?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:56.94,2:01:59.03,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 钱多吗? - 挺多的\N{\rEng}- Is there a lot of money? - There's a lot.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:59.03,2:02:01.32,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你现在能走了 - 我知道 你表现得太牛了\N{\rEng}- You can go now. - I know. You did amazing.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:01.32,2:02:03.74,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你现在可以去参赛了 - 我就知道你行 太棒了\N{\rEng}- You can go on your trip now. - I knew you could do this. So good.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:03.74,2:02:05.07,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你干得太漂亮了\N{\rEng}You did such a good job.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:05.08,2:02:07.08,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\rEng}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:07.79,2:02:10.87,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 亲爱的 你的预产期是什么时候? - 怎么了? 孩子没事吧?\N{\rEng}- Honey, when is your due date? - Why? Is the baby okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:10.87,2:02:12.79,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,孩子没大碍 我只需要你冷静点\N{\rEng}The baby is fine. I just need you to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:12.79,2:02:14.71,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你是她丈夫吗? - 不是 我是她朋友\N{\rEng}- Are you the husband? - No. I'm her friend.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:14.71,2:02:16.79,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,她还有四周就生了 孩子会没事吗?\N{\rEng}She's due in four weeks. The baby will be okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:16.80,2:02:18.38,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,孩子很安全 现在得说再见了\N{\rEng}The baby is okay. It's time to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:18.38,2:02:20.42,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我不能进去? - 手术室只准家属进\N{\rEng}- I can't go? - Only family in the operating room.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:20.42,2:02:22.09,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不 别别别别别!\N{\rEng}No, no, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:22.09,2:02:23.93,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,会没事的 瑞秋 没事的 真的没事的\N{\rEng}it's gonna be fine. Rachel, it's fine. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:23.93,2:02:26.05,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不 别别别! 马蒂 不要\N{\rEng}No, no, no! Marty, no.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:26.05,2:02:27.26,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他就在门外候着\N{\rEng}He'll be right outside.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:27.26,2:02:28.68,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,马蒂 不要!\N{\rEng}Marty, no!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:28.68,2:02:30.85,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,瑞秋 我进不去 他们说我不能进去\N{\rEng}Rachel, I can't go. They're telling me I can't go.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:30.85,2:02:32.44,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我不想让你... - 请冷静下来\N{\rEng}- I don't want you to-- - Please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:32.44,2:02:33.94,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 别走 求你了! - 请冷静点\N{\rEng}- Don't go, please! - Please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:33.94,2:02:36.48,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,求你别走! 马蒂!\N{\rEng}Please don't go! Marty!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:38.36,2:02:40.11,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不!\N{\rEng}No!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:48.04,2:02:49.95,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,多谢 欢迎来到日本 洛克威尔先生\N{\rEng}Thank you very much. Welcome to Japan, Mr. Rockwell.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:49.95,2:02:51.41,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢 - 谢谢\N{\rEng}- Thank you. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:19.54,2:04:21.34,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,毛瑟先生 毛瑟先生\N{\rEng}Mr. Mauser. Mr. Mauser.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:21.34,2:04:24.97,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,噢 洛克威尔先生说让你去队尾\N{\rEng}Ah. Mr. Rockwell says the back of the line.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:25.67,2:04:28.01,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他还不想正式开始\N{\rEng}He doesn't want to begin yet.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:02.75,2:05:06.21,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,该练练了 也该整口啤酒了\N{\rEng}Needs some practice. Needs a beer.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:06.22,2:05:08.76,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,赛斯先生? 赛斯先生\N{\rEng}Mr. Sethi? Mr. Sethi.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:08.76,2:05:10.68,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿 是我 我是马蒂·毛瑟\N{\rEng}Hey. It's me. It's Marty Mauser.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:10.68,2:05:12.76,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,怎么样? 实际上 看到你在这儿我挺惊讶的\N{\rEng}How you doing? I'm surprised to see you here, actually.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:12.76,2:05:14.85,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 怎么说? - 我不知道 我...\N{\rEng}- Why's that? - I don't know. I--
Dialogue: 0,2:05:14.85,2:05:16.14,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,咱们确实得宣传锦标赛\N{\rEng}We do have a tournament to promote.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:16.14,2:05:17.89,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嗯 当然 当然\N{\rEng}No, of course, of course.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:18.94,2:05:19.94,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:20.44,2:05:23.23,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我想我该为在伦敦时的表现向你道歉\N{\rEng}I think I owe you an apology for the way I acted in London.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:23.23,2:05:24.32,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我当时就是个混账\N{\rEng}I was a jackass.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:24.32,2:05:27.03,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,讲礼貌是基本准则 毛瑟先生\N{\rEng}There is such a thing as a code of courtesy, Mr. Mauser.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:27.03,2:05:28.11,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不 我知道 只是...\N{\rEng}No, I know. It's just--
Dialogue: 0,2:05:28.65,2:05:30.53,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,在我长大的地方 每个人都只顾自己\N{\rEng}It's every man for himself where I come from.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:30.53,2:05:31.70,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我就是在那样的环境下长大的 懂吗?\N{\rEng}That's just how I grew up. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:31.70,2:05:33.66,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,有时候我觉得自己甚至无法控制...\N{\rEng}And sometimes I feel like I don't even have control--
Dialogue: 0,2:05:33.66,2:05:35.41,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我对你的借口真的没兴趣\N{\rEng}I'm really not interested in your excuses.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:35.41,2:05:36.95,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不 不 知道 这不是借口\N{\rEng}No, no, I know. It's not an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:36.95,2:05:39.50,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,听着 重点是接下来的态度我会好得多\N{\rEng}Look, the point is I'm gonna proceed with a much better attitude.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:39.50,2:05:41.79,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,顺便说下 要是今天看到我在场上很无礼\N{\rEng}And by the way, if you see me acting rude up there today,
Dialogue: 0,2:05:41.79,2:05:44.67,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,那是人设 是按剧本演的 我会输个14比21\N{\rEng}that's a character. This is scripted. I'm gonna lose 21-14.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:44.67,2:05:48.01,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这不是玩真的 真正的我 那个讲礼貌的我 下周你就能见识到了\N{\rEng}This isn't a real thing. The real me, the polite me, you'll see next week.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:48.01,2:05:49.51,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 下周? - 锦标赛上\N{\rEng}- Next week? - At the championship.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:49.51,2:05:51.34,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你不参加锦标赛\N{\rEng}You're not playing in the championship.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:51.34,2:05:53.34,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 什么? - 你今年没资格参赛\N{\rEng}- What? - You're not participating this year.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:53.35,2:05:55.18,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不 不 不 我想你搞错了\N{\rEng}No, no, no. I think you're confused.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:55.18,2:05:57.64,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我参加这活动就是为了这事儿 这样我才能付清剩下的罚款\N{\rEng}That's what I'm doing the event for, so I can pay off the rest of my fine.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:57.64,2:05:59.14,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,马上跟我去见洛克威尔先生\N{\rEng}Come talk to Mr. Rockwell right now.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:59.14,2:06:01.31,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,锦标赛还有不到两周就开始了\N{\rEng}The tournament is less than two weeks away.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:01.31,2:06:03.81,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 分组已经定好了 - 不 咱们可以重排分组\N{\rEng}- All the bracketing has been set. - No, but we'll redo the bracketing.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:03.81,2:06:07.53,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我不会为一个自以为是的美国人就打乱整个赛程\N{\rEng}I'm not gonna tear up the entire schedule on behalf of one entitled American.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:07.53,2:06:09.74,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,不 赛斯先生 赛斯先生 听着...\N{\rEng}No, Mr. Sethi. Mr. Sethi. Look...
Dialogue: 0,2:06:09.74,2:06:10.82,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我人都在这儿了\N{\rEng}I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:10.82,2:06:14.03,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我想你不知道我来这儿费了多大劲\N{\rEng}I don't think you know how difficult that was, for me to come here.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:14.03,2:06:15.49,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我现在可是在日本\N{\rEng}I'm in Japan right now.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:15.49,2:06:17.87,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,恐怕你走得还不够远\N{\rEng}You haven't come far enough, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:18.45,2:06:19.54,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,什么?\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:19.54,2:06:21.87,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你来这儿纯属白费劲\N{\rEng}You have wasted your time coming here.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:23.67,2:06:25.75,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,简直不敢相信\N{\rEng}Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:11.30,2:07:15.05,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我远渡重洋来到日本\N{\rEng}I've traveled many miles here to Japan
Dialogue: 0,2:07:15.05,2:07:18.64,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,就是为了挑战我的宿敌 远藤!\N{\rEng}to challenge my great nemesis, Endo!
Dialogue: 0,2:07:23.35,2:07:26.10,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他说什么?\N{\rEng}What's he say?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:26.10,2:07:27.98,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他不想让你再丢人现眼了\N{\rEng}He doesn't want to embarrass you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:27.98,2:07:30.02,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,让我丢脸? 我早就没脸没皮了\N{\rEng}Embarrass me? I am beyond embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:30.03,2:07:33.99,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,告诉他他是个... 你们的冠军就是个骗子和怂包\N{\rEng}Tell him he's a-- Your champion is a fraud and a chicken.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:38.08,2:07:39.33,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他就是个怂包!\N{\rEng}He's chicken!
Dialogue: 0,2:07:41.12,2:07:43.58,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,远藤先生同意比试\N{\rEng}Mr. Endo agrees to the match.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:43.58,2:07:44.71,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,挺好\N{\rEng}Great.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:44.71,2:07:47.63,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,条件是...\N{\rEng}On the condition that...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:47.63,2:07:51.88,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,输家必须当着所有观众的面亲吻一头猪\N{\rEng}the loser has to kiss a pig in front of the entire audience.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:51.88,2:07:54.26,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 亲猪? - 是的\N{\rEng}- A pig? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:55.22,2:07:57.05,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,亲猪? 什么?\N{\rEng}A pig? What?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:57.05,2:07:59.97,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他说既然你要表现得像头猪\N{\rEng}He said if you are going to act like a pig,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:00.51,2:08:02.68,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他很乐意帮你配个种\N{\rEng}he will happily mate you with one.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:04.56,2:08:07.52,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,那他妈什么...\N{\rEng}What does that--
Dialogue: 0,2:08:31.55,2:08:33.46,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这他妈电线挡道了\N{\rEng}It's this cord in the fucking way.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:33.46,2:08:36.42,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我踩到线了 挪开点\N{\rEng}I'm stepping on the cord. Move the cord.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:36.43,2:08:38.80,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,把线往那边挪挪 省得我下次又滑倒!\N{\rEng}Move the cord over there so I don't slip on it next time!
Dialogue: 0,2:08:38.80,2:08:41.26,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 对不起 对不起 - 省得我折了脚踝!\N{\rEng}- I'm sorry. I'm sorry. - So I don't break my ankle!
Dialogue: 0,2:08:50.19,2:08:54.86,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,远藤! 远藤!\N{\rEng}Endo! Endo!
Dialogue: 0,2:09:23.26,2:09:25.01,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你会说英语吗? - 会\N{\rEng}- You speak English? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:25.02,2:09:26.27,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他在说什么?\N{\rEng}What's he saying?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:26.27,2:09:29.06,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,"我们欢迎一位特别嘉宾"\N{\rEng}"We are welcoming a special guest."
Dialogue: 0,2:09:32.02,2:09:34.69,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,"拉姆·赛斯先生 请上台"\N{\rEng}"Mr. Ram Sethi. Come on up."
Dialogue: 0,2:09:42.37,2:09:43.45,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:43.45,2:09:48.79,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,也谢谢洛克威尔先生 举办了这么一场令人难忘的活动\N{\rEng}And thank you, Mr. Rockwell, for hosting such an unforgettable event.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:49.33,2:09:54.96,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,咱们刚才看到的 只是下周精彩内容的一个预告\N{\rEng}What we have just witnessed is a mere taste of what is to come next week
Dialogue: 0,2:09:54.96,2:09:58.63,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,届时世界顶尖选手们将同台竞技\N{\rEng}when the finest players in the world will be competing
Dialogue: 0,2:09:58.63,2:10:02.59,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,挑战你们家乡的英雄 远藤琴音先生\N{\rEng}against your hometown hero, Koto Endo-san.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:09.35,2:10:13.44,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,废话不多说 请出小猪阿古\N{\rEng}No more words from me. Let's bring on Agu the pig
Dialogue: 0,2:10:13.44,2:10:16.44,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,看看这位美国人怎么亲它吧\N{\rEng}and see the American plant a kiss on him.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:20.07,2:10:22.57,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,"现在把猪请上台"\N{\rEng}"Now we bring the pig onto the stage."
Dialogue: 0,2:10:42.30,2:10:45.72,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,等等 等等 等等\N{\rEng}Wait, wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:46.43,2:10:47.93,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿\N{\rEng}Hey. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:47.93,2:10:49.72,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,亲猪之前 我想先跟他真刀真枪赛一场\N{\rEng}I want to play him in a real game first before I kiss the pig.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:49.73,2:10:50.98,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我想跟他真正较量一下\N{\rEng}I want to play him in a real game.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:51.52,2:10:53.77,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,告诉他 我想来场不掺水的比赛\N{\rEng}Tell him I want to play him in a game that's not a sham.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:55.31,2:10:56.52,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,告诉他!\N{\rEng}Tell him!
Dialogue: 0,2:10:57.48,2:11:00.15,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你 告诉观众 刚才那是假赛\N{\rEng}You, tell the audience that was a fake game.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:00.15,2:11:02.78,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,告诉他们刚才是在演戏 我想跟他来场认真的\N{\rEng}Tell them it was a sham and I want to play a real game against him.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:02.78,2:11:05.11,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 我办不到 - 为什么办不到?\N{\rEng}- I cannot do that for you. - Why can't you do that?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:05.12,2:11:08.41,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,刚才那是假赛 是排演好的\N{\rEng}That was a fake game. That was staged.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:08.41,2:11:10.20,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,没一点是真的\N{\rEng}No part of that was real.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:10.20,2:11:13.21,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我根本没发挥实力\N{\rEng}I was not playing to the best of my ability.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:13.21,2:11:16.92,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这是对在场所有人的极大不尊重\N{\rEng}It was an enormous form of disrespect to everyone here.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:16.92,2:11:19.34,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嘿 听着 谁想看真比赛?\N{\rEng}Hey, listen, who wants a real game?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:19.34,2:11:20.71,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,举手示意下 快点\N{\rEng}Show of hands. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:20.71,2:11:22.26,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,等等 这位先生 这位先生\N{\rEng}Wait, this man. This man.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:24.89,2:11:27.14,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,马蒂 你说得对 咱们想看真比赛!\N{\rEng}Marty, you're right. We want to see the real game!
Dialogue: 0,2:11:27.14,2:11:28.14,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,没错!\N{\rEng}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,2:11:37.02,2:11:39.65,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,远藤 你要站在他们那边?\N{\rEng}En-do, you're gonna side with them?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:39.65,2:11:41.36,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,翻译 翻译这句\N{\rEng}Translate. Translate this.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:41.36,2:11:43.07,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他真要站他们那边?\N{\rEng}He's gonna side with them, really?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:43.07,2:11:47.24,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,任由一家美国公司把他当吉祥物 压榨他的价值卖产品?\N{\rEng}An American company selling their product off of his back like he's a mascot?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:47.24,2:11:48.32,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你不是吉祥物\N{\rEng}You're not a mascot.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:48.33,2:11:49.91,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,布莱恩 把他带下去\N{\rEng}Brian, get him down.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:49.91,2:11:52.58,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,咱们来场真的 观众想看真比赛\N{\rEng}Let's give them a real game. They want a real game.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:52.58,2:11:53.83,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,好了 好了\N{\rEng}Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:53.83,2:11:56.00,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,谢谢 谢谢 咱们得继续流程\N{\rEng}Thank you, thank you. We need to move it along.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:56.00,2:11:57.88,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,下周锦标赛我参加不了了\N{\rEng}I'm not gonna be at the championship next week
Dialogue: 0,2:11:57.88,2:12:00.59,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,全拜这混蛋所赐 我打不了锦标赛\N{\rEng}'cause of this asshole. I'm not gonna be at the championship.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:00.59,2:12:03.05,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,给我个机会 你羞辱了我\N{\rEng}Give me a chance. You humiliated me.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:03.59,2:12:05.63,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,求你了 求你了 远藤 求你\N{\rEng}Please, please, Endo. Please.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:05.63,2:12:07.39,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 拜托了 就当帮我 行吗? - 好吧\N{\rEng}- Please, for me. Yes? - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:07.39,2:12:08.72,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 太好了 行 - 成了? 他答应了?\N{\rEng}- Yes. Okay. - Good? He says yes?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:08.72,2:12:09.89,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他答应了\N{\rEng}He says yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:09.89,2:12:11.56,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,谢谢 远藤 谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you, Endo. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:13.02,2:12:15.14,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,他答应了 耶\N{\rEng}He said yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:34.33,2:12:35.58,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,这小畜生\N{\rEng}This little fuck.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:35.58,2:12:36.58,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,开干吧\N{\rEng}Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:49.64,2:12:50.64,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,操\N{\rEng}Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:00.19,2:13:01.69,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,好了 马蒂 行吧\N{\rEng}Okay, Marty. All right.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:48.57,2:13:49.57,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,耶!\N{\rEng}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,2:13:50.66,2:13:52.70,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,耶 马蒂! 上啊 小伙子!\N{\rEng}Yeah, Marty! Go boy!
Dialogue: 0,2:14:51.93,2:14:53.89,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,省省唾沫吧 我知道我拿不到钱\N{\rEng}You can save your breath. I know I'm not getting paid.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:53.89,2:14:56.18,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,赢也好输也好 你一分钱都拿不到 我倒想看看你怎么回家\N{\rEng}Win or lose, you get nothing. I wonder how you're gonna get home.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:56.18,2:14:58.18,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你别想上我的飞机 - 没关系 好吗?\N{\rEng}- You're not getting on my plane. - It doesn't matter, okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:58.18,2:15:00.81,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,除非你打算取消活动 否则咱们没什么好谈的\N{\rEng}Unless you're planning on shutting down the event, we got nothing to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:00.81,2:15:02.69,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 你觉得就这么简单? - 对 我就这么觉得\N{\rEng}- You think it's that simple? - Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:03.40,2:15:05.15,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,让我来给你解释一下\N{\rEng}Let me explain to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:05.77,2:15:10.99,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我生于1601年 我是个吸血鬼 我活了很久很久了\N{\rEng}I was born in 1601. I'm a vampire. I've been around forever.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:11.57,2:15:13.70,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,几个世纪以来 我见过很多像马蒂·毛瑟这样的人\N{\rEng}I've met many Marty Mausers over the centuries.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:13.70,2:15:16.49,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,有些跟我作对 有些不走正道 他们不诚实\N{\rEng}Some of them crossed me, some weren't straight. They weren't honest.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:16.49,2:15:18.70,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,而正是这类人 才能一直活到现在\N{\rEng}And those are the ones that are still here.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:18.70,2:15:21.62,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你去赢下那场比赛 你也会永远留在这里\N{\rEng}You go out and win that game, you're gonna be here forever too.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:21.62,2:15:24.46,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,而且你永远不会快乐 你永远不会快乐的\N{\rEng}And you'll never be happy. You will never be happy.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:26.54,2:15:27.75,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,好吧 洛克威尔先生\N{\rEng}Okay, Mr. Rockwell.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:38.22,2:15:47.40,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,远藤! 远藤! 远藤!\N{\rEng}Endo! Endo! Endo!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:15.97,2:16:17.55,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,开始了!\N{\rEng}There we go!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:05.93,2:17:08.31,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你他妈开玩笑呢吧\N{\rEng}You gotta fucking kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:27.71,2:17:28.83,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,赛点\N{\rEng}Match point.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:09.02,2:19:11.81,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 别让他逮到你 马蒂! - 耶 马蒂! 上啊 小伙子!\N{\rEng}- Don't let him getcha, Marty! - Yeah, Marty! Go boy!
Dialogue: 0,2:19:52.06,2:19:53.23,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:53.23,2:19:55.52,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,谢谢 精彩的比赛 精彩的比赛\N{\rEng}Thank you. Good game. Good game.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:55.52,2:19:56.69,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你是个伟大的选手\N{\rEng}You're a great player.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:58.23,2:20:00.65,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,祝你在锦标赛好运 行吗? 希望你能赢\N{\rEng}Good luck at the championship, okay? I hope you win.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:48.20,2:20:50.20,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,贝尔维尤医院 有什么可以帮您?\N{\rEng}Bellevue Hospital. May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:50.20,2:20:51.28,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,嗨 是的\N{\rEng}Hi, yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:51.29,2:20:53.54,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,我想找瑞秋·米兹勒接个电话 谢谢?\N{\rEng}I was hoping to be connected with Rachel Mizler, please?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:53.54,2:20:55.29,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,您知道她在几楼吗?\N{\rEng}Do you know what floor she's on?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:55.29,2:20:57.33,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,额 她应该刚做完手术\N{\rEng}Well, she would have gotten out of surgery.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:57.33,2:20:59.38,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,就是你们安置这类人的地方\N{\rEng}So wherever you keep people like that.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:59.38,2:21:00.67,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:01.46,2:21:05.30,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,目前看来 她昨晚被转到了产科病房\N{\rEng}So it looks like she was moved to the maternity ward last night.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:05.30,2:21:07.18,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 产科病房? - 是的\N{\rEng}- The maternity ward?- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:07.18,2:21:09.93,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- “产科病房”是什么意思? - 抱歉 我不清楚细节\N{\rEng}- What do you mean, "the maternity ward"?- I'm sorry, I don't know the details.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:09.93,2:21:12.22,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,她还好吗? 孩子生了吗? 离预产期还有四周呢\N{\rEng}Is she okay? Did she have the baby? She's not due for four weeks.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:12.22,2:21:15.22,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,我只有这些信息 她是被急救送进来的...\N{\rEng}This is all the information that I have, that she was rushed--
Dialogue: 0,2:21:15.23,2:21:17.39,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,“急救”? 你说什么“急救”? 你刚才还说“转到”\N{\rEng}"Rushed"? What are you saying, "rushed"? First you said, "moved,"
Dialogue: 0,2:21:17.39,2:21:19.48,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 现在又说“急救”? - 先生 请您冷静点好吗?\N{\rEng}- now you're saying, "rushed"?- Sir, can you please calm down?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:19.48,2:21:22.19,OffscreenBottom,,0,0,0,,直接帮我转产科病房 谢谢\N{\rEng}Just put me through to the maternity ward, please.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:22.19,2:21:24.11,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 爸爸! - 嘿!\N{\rEng}- Daddy! - Hey!
Dialogue: 0,2:21:42.84,2:21:44.59,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,打扰下 产科病房是在这儿吗?\N{\rEng}Excuse me. Maternity ward's here?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:44.59,2:21:46.17,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 是的 顺着走廊走 - 谢谢\N{\rEng}- Yes, down the hall. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:46.17,2:21:48.26,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,- 先生 您得登记一下 - 不 不 我是父亲\N{\rEng}- Sir, you need to sign in. - No, no. I'm the father.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:54.39,2:21:55.39,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\rEng}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:37.47,2:22:40.14,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,没事了 睡吧 我在呢 我在这儿 没事的\N{\rEng}It's okay, sleep. I'm here. I'm here. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:42.02,2:22:44.65,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我就在这里 别担心 我哪儿也不去\N{\rEng}I'm right here. Don't worry, I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:44.65,2:22:45.82,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,睡吧\N{\rEng}Go back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:46.44,2:22:47.69,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\rEng}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:43.62,2:23:45.00,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,五号床 谢谢 米兹勒\N{\rEng}Five, please, Mizler.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:01.68,2:24:03.19,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,你想让我抱抱他吗?\N{\rEng}Do you want me to pick him up?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:22.12,2:24:23.75,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,跟爸爸打个招呼\N{\rEng}Say hi to Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:29.59,2:24:31.96,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,是的 他在这儿呢 喊爸爸\N{\rEng}Yeah, there he is. Say hi.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:42.39,2:24:44.68,DialogueBottom,,0,0,0,,嗯 对\N{\rEng}Yes. Yeah.
